	(28,4,'2015-12-22 16:19:56','2015-12-22 16:19:56','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There’s a trend developing - and homeowners are starting to notice. What was once considered a benefit or luxury has now become the norm; a norm that buyers and agents alike are placing at the top of their must-have list when searching for the next move.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The trend? Smart homes. More specifically, smart home kitchens. </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.coldwellbanker.ca/press-release/smarthomes\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A study by Coldwell Banker Real Estate</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> found that 62 percent of agents are seeing more buyers interested in managing and controlling the technology in their home through a device - a smartphone or tablet - more than they were just two years ago. The United States leads the way in overall smart home adoption, with the estimated number of smart homes estimated to rise from 4.6 million to 24.5 million in just five years.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And kitchens? Smart kitchens and connected appliances are smarter, sleeker and greener than they ever have been. As an innovator, you owe it to yourself to stay ahead of your peers and give connected cooking a try, right? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Right. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you’re ready to take the leap into building your smart home kitchen, our top 10 must-have items are here. These products were selected by reviewing hundreds of product and review sites, taking the highest average review for each and every selection. Not only are they effective and innovative, they’re pushing the boundaries of the smart home and are prepared to make your kitchen greater than every before.</span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374411&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Mr.+Coffee%27s+WeMo-enabled+Smart\">1. Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker</a></span></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Because everyone needs a morning cup of coffee, right? We love this Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enable Coffeemaker. It\'s a high-quality coffeemaker that you can control with either your smartphone or your tablet, allowing you to set automated brewing schedules. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And the best part? You can receive push notifications when your coffee\'s ready, which makes your morning alarm so much easier.  </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Owners and reviewers alike are impressed by the Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker. Why? Scheduling and adjusting brew time and set-up reminders is a huge bonus, according to </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374411&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Mr.+Coffee%27s+WeMo-enabled+Smart\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reviewers on Amazon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“This machine has a lot of possibilities,” one reviewer said. “The one advantage this has is the Wemo app allows you to schedule one brew in your coffee maker each day of the week.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to the scheduler, this unit also brews coffee in under 7 minutes, and heats water to the optimal temperature. Manual operation is available (but who wouldn’t want to automate the brewing process?)  </span>\r\n<h1><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Egg-Minder-Wink-App-Enabled-Smart\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Egg Minder Wink App-Enabled Smart Egg Tray</span></a></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You know when you’re just not quite sure if the eggs in your fridge are still in good shape to eat? This item will solve your morning grind. The Egg Minder was a Kickstarter success story. Not only will it keep count of your eggs, it will tell you which ones are the oldest and which ones are going bad. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Egg Minder Wink App-Enabled Smart Egg Tray Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers are in awe at this egg tray - and likely wonder why they hadn’t thought of it before. Although it’s such a simple product, reviewers love the in-tray LED lights that indicate the oldest egg, and the addition of push notifications that alert you when you\'re running low. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The best part? Amazon reviewers love that this device is  IFTTT compatible, so you can set up some great IoT combos. For example example, \"If I run out of eggs, play Hotline Bling on Spotify.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How great is that?</span>\r\n<h1><a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/irobot-scooba-450/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. iRobot Scooba 450</span></a></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although the iRobot Scooba 450 might look like a Roomba, it certainly isn’t. Spoiler alert: The Scooba does more than just vacuum. It uses a three-cycle process to soak, scrub and dry your floors, essentially replacing the mopping process. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>iRobot Scooba 450 Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/irobot-scooba-450/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers on CNET</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> have replaced their well-used cleaning accessories. Why? “iRobot\'s Scooba 450 really can replace your old mop and bucket. Separate tanks mean that dirty water doesn\'t get recycled back onto your floors”, which makes it a win/win for time and efficiency. </span>\r\n\r\nTwo room size options are available with this device - 150 square feet for 20 minutes of cleaning or 300 square feet for 40 minutes of cleaning, meaning you’ll find that this works for virtually any room in your home.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even better? Battery indicator lights ensure you’ll never run out of battery life. </span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/ref=sr_1_1?s=kitchen&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374965&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=anova\">4. Anova Sous Vide </a></span></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sous Vide Precision cooking is a relatively new concept, but one that home cookers often swear by. Why? It’s essentially fool proof. Precision cookers make it easy to get professional results at home, circulating water around the pot while ensuring consistent temperatures throughout your ingredients. The best part is that the precision cooker also connects to your phone, allowing you to cook your meals with the touch of a button. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Anova Sous Vide Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Who wouldn’t want this? </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another time, I was working on a project and had just enough time to stop home for about 10 minutes. I bagged up some pork loin, tossed it in the stock pot filled with water, turned on the circulator, and headed back out for a couple hours. Came home, cooked some noodles and veggies and 15 mins later, had food ready to go. - </span></i><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/ref=sr_1_1?s=kitchen&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374965&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=anova\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon Review </span></i></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers love the Anova Sous Vide. It’s easy - offering a stainless steel skirt, which can be removed and cleaned in the dishwasher - and connected with your smartphone, as cooking notifications are sent as your meal is cooking, which allows you to monitor progress remotely </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Precision cooking holds food at a precise temperature so there is no worry about overcooking your meal. That sounds like a win for home chefs. </span>\r\n<h1><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. First Alert OneLink</span></a></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every kitchen needs a smoke detector, and First Alert is making this as easy as ever. The entire suite of products from First Alert are all compatible with Apple\'s HomeKit system and can be controlled via iPhone. It’s a win/win, and a safety precaution. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>First Alert OneLink Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Safety and security are top of mind for reviewers online. Low battery warning and end of life timer make this product safe and secure, which is exactly what you need in your home connected kitchen. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wireless enabled, this battery operated detector creates a wireless safety network. The detector is also designed to provide you the earliest warning in an emergency, providing “peace of mind” according to </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reviewers on Amazon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n<h1><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6. Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker</span></a></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Similar to the Anova Sous Vide, this Crock Pot Smart Slow Cooker is seriously a lifesaver. This device connects via Wi-Fi and can be monitored and turned on and off using an iOS or Android mobile device, allowing you to control your dinner from the office. As well, you can also use an app to adjust temperature and timing on the fly, so if you’re getting home earlier than expected, you can easily adjust the speed well ahead of time. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“I did not know a slow cooker could be so high tech”, said </span><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">one reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We totally agree. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With remote access to all cooking functions, anywhere - and anytime - the Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker offers adjustable cooking time and temperature from your smart device, which is great for on-the-go home chefs. </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Wemo allowed me to remotely start and stop my meal, check how long it had been cooking and change the heat setting or turn it off.”</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> - </span><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crock-Pot.ca Review </span></a>\r\n<h1><a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/idevices-igrill-mini/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">7. iGrill Mini</span></a></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The iGrill Mini is a Bluetooth thermometer that allows you to check on the progress of your meal right from your smartphone. (We love smartphone enabled cooking devices, can’t you tell?) A companion app includes recommended cooking temperatures for just about every protein you can think of, which saves tons of time as you’re quickly whipping up your meal.  </span>\r\n\r\n<b>iGrill Mini Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The first thing I noticed about iGrill Mini is its diminutive size -- it measures just 2 inches by 2 inches,” </span><a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/idevices-igrill-mini/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">said one CNET reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. “It\'s just a cute, compact gadget with a lot of functionality packed into its small frame.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Online reviewers agree that it’s simple to set-up with smartphone devices, and promises to cook food without needing to check manually. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even better? You can select from among various presets categorized by temperature, making each and every recipe easier than the last. </span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC\">8. HAPIfork Bluetooth-Enabled Smart Fork</a></span></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A smart fork that helps you monitor and track your eating habits? It’s possible, and it’s here. This connected cutlery measures just how many mouthfuls you take during your meal, buzzing and flashing if you’re eating too quickly.  There’s also a great dashboard that lets you look back and analyzing your overall performance. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>HAPIfork Bluetooth-Enabled Smart Fork Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Wow, what a great product! Before I owned a HAPIfork, I could never tell when I was eating too fast,” says this </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\nStatistics are available in real time, so you can review your analysis immediately. Een better? Set your workout objectives, track your progress and score points through the program.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And to share your results with friends? HAPI moments can be shared online, for your friends and followers to see. </span>\r\n<h1><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">9. Prep Pad from the Orange Chef </span></a></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prep Pad offers nutritional tracking with a twist. Tallying up nutritional info from the foods added to any bowl on its connected food scale, this product can tell you exactly how many carb, fat and protein calories are in your food. It truly makes meal prep so much easier.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Prep Pad from the Orange Chef Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The Prep Pad is easily one of my favorite tech + food products. Not only does it help me keep track of what I\'m eating, but it also helps me create a nutritional information sheet for my own recipes.” - </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon Reviewer</span></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Prep Pad gives you an overview of every ingredient you put on the food scale, allowing you to access a food library of more than 300,000 items. And like the Amazon reviewer said, you can track and log meals through your smartphone.</span>\r\n<h1><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10. LG’s Smart Oven</span></a></h1>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We saved the biggest for last because we just needed to include LG’s smart oven in our list. This is truly the creme of the crop in the connected, smart kitchen. This connected kitchen appliance will allow you to gain control remotely from your smartphone. The best part? The accompanying app allows you to set it and (nearly) forget it - all while sending recipes to your range. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>LG’s Smart Oven Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The LG Smart Oven has left users “</span><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">totally satisfied with the range</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">”. With great features, including even cooking and a large oven, you can set precise temperature control remotely. The infrared grill system and the true convection oven have given this product a </span><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4.9 star review online</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The smart home kitchen is here - and it’s here to stay. With innovative and revolutionary products emerging from start-up organizations to large corporations alike, smart kitchen products are developing at a rapid rate. We’re excited to join this remarkable ride ahead.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','10 Must-Have Items for a Smart Home Kitchen','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-revision-v1','','','2015-12-22 16:19:56','2015-12-22 16:19:56','',17,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/2015/12/22/17-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
