as decorative.\r\n\r\nLikewise, upgrading the functionality of your space with the latest technology has a big impact in this room. You’ll use your shower and bathroom faucet on a daily basis, so upgrading them with cool tech features will be something you constantly get to enjoy.\r\n<h5><em>Have you recently upgraded your master bathroom? Have any experience with the products listed above, or a few of your own to add to our list? We’d love to hear about your adventures in “no renovations required” upgrades! </em></h5>','No Renovations Required: 9 Modern Products for a Smarter, Sexier Bathroom','','inherit','closed','closed','','90-revision-v1','','','2016-01-03 00:33:11','2016-01-03 00:33:11','',90,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/2016/01/03/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
