ur home that will provide safety, security and ease for yourself and your visitors.','Top 5 Best Smart Home Locks','','inherit','closed','closed','','136-revision-v1','','','2016-01-03 18:19:24','2016-01-03 18:19:24','',136,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/03/136-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(155,6,'2016-01-03 18:20:25','2016-01-03 18:20:25','Smart home door locks are arguably one of the most comforting items you can have in your home. Not only can they automatically detect your presence and provide safety while you\'re away, they can also send electronic keys to friends and family that will only work during specified hours, allowing you to let just about anyone you trust into your home while you\'re unable to answer the door.\r\n\r\n<strong>Isn\'t that so much better than your traditional, conventional key locks? </strong>\r\n\r\nIf you\'re considering purchasing a smart home door lock as your next purchase, you should certainly know your options. With so many products on the market, from price points to feature sets, be sure to explore the best option for you.\r\n\r\nIn this blog, we\'ve put together the five best smart home locks based on price point, <strong>with all locks being under $300</strong>. To not spoil the surprise, we\'re counting down from #5, all the way through to the top spot.\r\n\r\nRead on.\r\n<h1>Top 5 Smart Home Decor Locks Under $300:</h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>5. <a href=\"https://lockitron.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Lockitron</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Lockitron-Keyless-Entry-Using-Phone/dp/B00L3WUUMW/ref=cm_cr_pr_product_top?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://www.wareable.com/media/images/2015/07/1-lockitron-1436375698-Hyk1-full-width-inline.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></a>\r\n\r\nLockitron\'s \'The Bolt\' is the second generation product from the brand. The Bolt has learned from previous bugs in their product, and has released a new and improved smart home lock innovation. This product works wirelessly with both Buetooth and Wi-Fi, which means that users have two options in the opening experience, plus the ability to lock or unlock your home for anyone - be it friends, family or a parcel delivery.\r\n\r\n<a style=\"line-height: 1.5;\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/August-Smart-Lock-Keyless-Smartphone/dp/B00QI6FVIQ%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAJ3NOW7JKGQLTEY4A%26tag%3Dcnet-api-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00QI6FVIQ\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"Bluetooth 4.0 is always on and detects your device when you approach it and have the Lockitron App open on your phone\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>“It can sense if your door has been unlocked, dutifully notifying you immediately.”</em>\r\n\r\n<em>“ You can pay for your coffee, turn off your lights, control your TV, and start your car with your smartphone — so why can\'t you unlock your doors? That\'s exactly what Lockitron does. ”</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nThe big sell for us is the price point. This smart lock runs around $99 which, for the features available, is impressive. We love that \"The Bolt\" has all of the options available from the \'big guys\' - unlocking your home from anywhere in the world, email notifications when batteries are running low and super easy installation. It\'s a great smart home lock to try on your own.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>4. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/OKIDOKEYS-SMART-LOCK-Bluetooth-Smartphone-Compatible/dp/B00IVKGF3C/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">OKIDOKEYS Classic</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/OKIDOKEYS-SMART-LOCK-Bluetooth-Smartphone-Compatible/dp/B00IVKGF3C/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://cdn.toptenreviews.com/rev/prod/large/60621-okidokeys-smart-lock-box.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWith the OKIDOKEY Classic, your phone becomes your key, working with multiple Android and iOS phones. The product promises easy installation in just a \"few minutes\", with no drilling required. From creating a key for your babysitter to defining specific entry times for mail delivery, the OKIDOKEY Classic provides safe, easy access to your home.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/August-Smart-Lock-Keyless-Smartphone/dp/B00QI6FVIQ%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAJ3NOW7JKGQLTEY4A%26tag%3Dcnet-api-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00QI6FVIQ\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"I\'ve loved my experience with Okidokeys locks (I got 2 access packs). Installing was as I would expect, I pulled it out and starting slapping it together, when I had a problem I read the directions and watched the install video. Magic, it worked.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"This is an absolutely BRILLIANT product!\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"I installed the Smart Lock yesterday. It took me about 5 minutes to install after I read thru everything first. It works great for my family.\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nOKIDOKEYS offers 6 opening rules to fit your needs, which is something that stood out to us. Among these opening rules is a hands-free mode that unlocks the door automatically when you are close to it (think of the auto-opening door that Tesla offers). The best part? This lock features a built-in alarm that notifies you when an intruder, or someone you\'re not expecting, attempts to enter your door. We love the safety and security this lock offers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>3. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Danalock-Integrated-Smartlock-Bluetooth-Compatible/dp/B00K4HRQBK/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Danalock</a></strong></h3>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Danalock-Integrated-Smartlock-Bluetooth-Compatible/dp/B00K4HRQBK/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://www.wareable.com/media/images/2015/07/1-danalock-1436375710-eE7i-full-width-inline.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></a></h3>\r\nThe Danalock from Denmark promises great design for both the product and the app, something that home owners are always searching for when finding a smart home lock. Rest assured, although this product is from Denmark, it does come in SKUs to fit all sorts of European and North American doors with wireless and connectivity standards to match. The product promises patented, highest level of encrypted security available.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/August-Smart-Lock-Keyless-Smartphone/dp/B00QI6FVIQ%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAJ3NOW7JKGQLTEY4A%26tag%3Dcnet-api-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00QI6FVIQ\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"The Danalock is beautifully designed, and looks on the outside much like the August smart lock.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"This was a cinch to install. I got mine installed in about 20 minutes after I read the instructions and downloaded the app.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"It was not at all complicated to install. The instructions were very clear. I am very excited about this product!\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nWe love the design of this product. The Danalock has not fallen short in any capacity throughout the design and technology process. It also looks incredibly easy - all you need to do is supply the orders to your lock directly from your smartphone or computer, and schedule entry for yourself or others. According to reviews online, installation is straight-forward, with great support available.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>2. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Kwikset-Cylinder-Bluetooth-Enabled-Deadbolt/dp/B00CPTD5AQ/\" target=\"_blank\">Kwikset Kevo</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Kwikset-Cylinder-Bluetooth-Enabled-Deadbolt/dp/B00CPTD5AQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://www.wareable.com/media/images/2015/07/2-kevo-spl2-1436376090-nXGp-full-width-inline.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"905\" height=\"510\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Kwikset Kevo is just about the gold standard on the market. Not only has it been around for a significant period of time, but it also has some big pluses - like self-install, free, unlimited guest eKeys, and a lengthy history of notifications to tell you who as entered. The Kwikset Kevo allows you to leave your smartphone in your pocket or purse upon entering your, making sure you\'ll never have to fumble for keys again.  Convenient, isn\'t it?\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/August-Smart-Lock-Keyless-Smartphone/dp/B00QI6FVIQ%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAJ3NOW7JKGQLTEY4A%26tag%3Dcnet-api-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00QI6FVIQ\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"This product has saved my bacon many times, especially when carrying something heavy/cumbersome. I cannot tell you how integrated this lock is my daily routine. \"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Installation and setup was quick and pretty painless. We rekeyed both new locks with our existing Kwikset key.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"The installation instructions were flawless, and all the hardware needed was present. The only tool you need is a screwdriver.\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Kwikset Kevo has been on the market for a lengthy period of time, meaning that many of the natural bugs in smart home locks have already been worked through. The greatest bonus that we love is that this lock looks fairly normal from the outside - it\'s a definite bonus, as it\'s not a distraction to passerby\'s or neighbors.\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><strong>1. <a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/august-smart-lock/\" target=\"_blank\">August Smart Lock</a></strong></h3>\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/August-AUG-SL01-M01-G01-electronic-keyless-access/dp/B00QI6FVIQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/61VmYxoWcnL._SL1000_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" /></a></strong>\r\nWith over 140 reviews on Amazon alone, the August Smart Lock is one of the most popular locks in this price range. The August Smart Lock allows you to lock and unlock your door, create virtual keys for family and friends and keep a close eye on who comes and goes. A 24/7 activity log (available on your smartphone) tracks who enters and exits your home, so you’ll always know who opens your door and when.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/August-Smart-Lock-Keyless-Smartphone/dp/B00QI6FVIQ%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAJ3NOW7JKGQLTEY4A%26tag%3Dcnet-api-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00QI6FVIQ\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"Good looks, strong user management, and convenient automated features make the August Smart Lock a leader in its niche.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"The August app allows you to easily lock or unlock August Smart Lock with a single tap once you’ve selected the lock—It allows you to add and add multiple locks. The user interface is well designed and makes using the app a pleasant experience.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Installation was simple with the included instructions and took under twenty minutes. Simple and easy.\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nThe asking price puts August on the more expensive side of the smart lock spectrum, but the reviewers aren\'t lying. This product is extremely easy to connect, as your exterior door hardware stays the same. There is nothing to wire or connect. When batteries need replacing, you’ll be notified by the app.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n<h3>In conclusion...</h3>\r\nSmart home door locks are emerging on the market quicker than ever, which means greater competition in the marketplace. With so many options available, we are sure there will be new, innovative products in months to come. These five smart home door locks under $300 are great options for your home that will provide safety, security and ease for yourself and your visitors.','Top 5 Best Smart Home Locks','','inherit','closed','closed','','136-revision-v1','','','2016-01-03 18:20:25','2016-01-03 18:20:25','',136,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/03/136-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
