use it is such a small space. Consider which pieces are most functional within the space. For example, a nice trashcan in a larger room might not have as much impact as it would in the bathroom where its presence is functional as well as decorative.\r\n\r\nLikewise, upgrading the functionality of your space with the latest technology has a big impact in this room. You’ll use your shower and bathroom faucet on a daily basis, so upgrading them with cool tech features will be something you constantly get to enjoy.\r\n<h5><em>Have you recently upgraded your master bathroom? Have any experience with the products listed above, or a few of your own to add to our list? We’d love to hear about your adventures in “no renovations required” upgrades! </em></h5>','No Renovations Required: 9 Modern Products for a Smarter, Sexier Bathroom','','inherit','closed','closed','','90-revision-v1','','','2016-01-04 01:49:01','2016-01-04 01:49:01','',90,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/04/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(171,4,'2016-01-04 01:49:30','2016-01-04 01:49:30','Bathrooms are notoriously expensive and labor-intensive to remodel when major renovations are involved. Once you start using words like <em>gut, repipe, </em>and <em>demo</em> you’re headed down a potentially long and costly road. In fact, <a href=\"http://www.remodeling.hw.net/benchmarks/cost-vs-value-nothing-average-here_o\">Remodeling Magazine recently reported</a> that the cost for an average bathroom remodel could range anywhere between $13,000 and a whopping $61,000. While a full remodel can add a lot of value to your home, we know that sometimes that isn’t in the budget.\r\n\r\nSo, what do you do when you’re craving a change to your en suite, but don’t have the time or budget for a total renovation? Scout products that can upgrade your space without having to hire a contractor or knock down any walls! By combining high quality décor items with some of the latest in smart home technology, you can create a whole new, exciting look and feel for your bathroom. You’ll be amazed what a few simple upgrades can do to make this space feel less like the family bathroom and more like a zen spa retreat.\r\n<h2><strong>We’ve compiled a list of nine awesome products which can give your bathroom a major facelift without having to do any major renovations.  </strong></h2>\r\nWe love a sleek and modern aesthetic, especially in a bathroom. We’ve chosen products for this list based on that style, and we’re pretty sure you’re going to love them as much as we do! While the following products range in price (anywhere from $50-$1,500) they all make a bold statement and provide a serious upgrade with minimal installation requirements.\r\n\r\nWe’ve also scouted some of the latest in smart home products, which are high-impact in a bathroom setting. Technology is allowing us to automate everything, including the temperature and pressure of our showers! In addition to these gadgets, this list includes a variety of sexy décor options which will add a sense of relaxation and beauty to your space.\r\n\r\nThe products on this list were selected because of their unique qualities and high-impact nature. Our choices were also based on great customer reviews from sites like Amazon.com and AllModern.com.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>1. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Moen-TS3420ORB-Digital-Vertical-Control/dp/B004SR3TOA/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449735904&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=moen+vertical+spa\" target=\"_blank\">Moen Vertical Shower Spa</a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Moen-TS3420ORB-Digital-Vertical-Control/dp/B004SR3TOA/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449735904&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=moen+vertical+spa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-103\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-113\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/moen-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFor a smarter shower, this Moen system allows you to control not only the exact temperature of your water but also the pressure level and number of sprays. You can control your experience on this sleek wall-mounted device, which is an upgrade for your shower’s appearance as well as its quality.\r\n<h3>2. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Smart-Weigh-Precision-Technology-Backlight/dp/B00FJ8PI3M/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449390946&amp;sr=8-2&amp;keywords=smart+home+bathroom\" target=\"_blank\">Smart Weigh Scale</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/71ocZ1WeeTL._SL1500_.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-123\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-123\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/71ocZ1WeeTL._SL1500_-700x652.jpg\" alt=\"71ocZ1WeeTL._SL1500_\" width=\"500\" height=\"466\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThis lightweight glass scale boasts a modern look while incorporating smart technology. It can measure weight with incredible accuracy, helping you to manage your fitness without worrying about a faulty scale.\r\n<h3>3. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/561T-DST-Compel-Bathroom-Touch2O-Technology/dp/B00UOOBUTM/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449736745&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=Delta+smart+touch+bathroom\" target=\"_blank\">Delta Bathroom Faucet Touch 2.0 </a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/41X-pyr3PzL.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-118\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-118\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/41X-pyr3PzL.jpg\" alt=\"41X-pyr3PzL\" width=\"266\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\nUpgrading to a high-end faucet is a simple way to make a big impact in your bathroom. This one looks beautiful, and also adds that extra touch of tech to wow your guests. By simply touching any part of the faucet or waving your hands within 4 inches of it, water begins to flow.\r\n<h3>4. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/K-9245-CP-Showerhead-Wireless-Speaker-Polished/dp/B00A46X48A/ref=sr_1_31?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449392008&amp;sr=8-31&amp;keywords=shower+speaker+smart\" target=\"_blank\">Showerhead with Speaker</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/61cG2HhhniL._SL1317_.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-121\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-121\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/61cG2HhhniL._SL1317_-700x742.jpg\" alt=\"61cG2HhhniL._SL1317_\" width=\"500\" height=\"530\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSo you love to sing in the shower, who doesn’t? Make your daily concerts sound <em>way </em>better with this Kohler showerhead. It includes a wireless speaker that syncs with Bluetooth-enabled devices, so you can play your favorite songs to your heart’s content. The speaker itself is also removable, and can be used in any other room of the house or on the go.\r\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Alessi-Birillo-Bathroom-Waste-Bin-PL10-W-AAS2740.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bathroom Trashcan</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/BirilloBathroomWasteBinbyPieroLissoni-2.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-126\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-126\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/BirilloBathroomWasteBinbyPieroLissoni-2.jpg\" alt=\"Birillo+Bathroom+Waste+Bin+by+Piero+Lissoni\" /></a>\r\n\r\nIn a room as small as a bathroom, each piece is important. This sleek, modern trashcan is a great finishing touch to your space. The simple-yet-functional design will blend seamlessly with your Smart House aesthetic.\r\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Oslo-Vanity-Bathroom-Mirror-with-Shelves-FHWA2432BK-DNB2001.html\" target=\"_blank\">Bathroom Mirror with Shelves</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/DanyaBE284A2Oslo-24X31.522VanityBathroomMirrorwithShelves-Black-2.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-128\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-128\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/DanyaBE284A2Oslo-24X31.522VanityBathroomMirrorwithShelves-Black-2.jpg\" alt=\"Danya+B%E2%84%A2+Oslo-+24+X+31.5%22+Vanity+Bathroom+Mirror+with+Shelves+-+Black\" /></a>\r\n\r\nIf you’re not up for removing and replacing your entire bathroom vanity, swapping out the mirror above the one you have is a simple-but-impactful alternative. This one from All Modern also adds functionality with shelves.\r\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2-TXN1558.html\" target=\"_blank\">Orchids Set</a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-109\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-109 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2.jpg\" alt=\"Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /></a>\r\n\r\nA few well-placed pieces of décor can add a lot to a small space. These faux orchids fit in with the modern, sexy vibe you’re looking for while adding a touch of softness to the space.\r\n<h3>8. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-ADAN1029.html\" target=\"_blank\">Quote Candle</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-2.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-130\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-130\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-2.jpg\" alt=\"Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nA candlelit bath is good for the soul, and this votive comes with an inspirational quote to help get you into a state of true zen.\r\n<h3>9. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Trademark-Fine-Art-Zen-Lotus-by-Kurt-Shaffer-Photographic-Print-on-Canvas-KS024-TMK4761.html\" target=\"_blank\">Zen Wall Art</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/41ySX9dNJWL._SY355_-1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-119\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-119\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/41ySX9dNJWL._SY355_-1.jpg\" alt=\"41ySX9dNJWL._SY355_\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFinally, when you don’t want to go through a major renovation, one of the simplest ways to upgrade a space is to add artwork to the walls. We love this romantic lotus print for an added sense of sexy sophistication.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith the addition of just a few products, you can change the look and feel of your bathroom drastically. It’s all about choosing a style and sticking with it, and knowing which pieces will give you the biggest bang for your buck. Luckily, in a bathroom setting figuring out which pieces to go with is fairly simple because it is such a small space. Consider which pieces are most functional within the space. For example, a nice trashcan in a larger room might not have as much impact as it would in the bathroom where its presence is functional as well as decorative.\r\n\r\nLikewise, upgrading the functionality of your space with the latest technology has a big impact in this room. You’ll use your shower and bathroom faucet on a daily basis, so upgrading them with cool tech features will be something you constantly get to enjoy.\r\n<h5><em>Have you recently upgraded your master bathroom? Have any experience with the products listed above, or a few of your own to add to our list? We’d love to hear about your adventures in “no renovations required” upgrades! </em></h5>','No Renovations Required: 9 Modern Products for a Smarter, Sexier Bathroom','','inherit','closed','closed','','90-revision-v1','','','2016-01-04 01:49:30','2016-01-04 01:49:30','',90,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/04/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
