VALUES
	(179,4,'2016-01-08 16:42:53','2016-01-08 16:42:53','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There’s a trend developing - and homeowners are starting to notice. What was once considered a benefit or luxury has now become the norm; a norm that buyers and agents alike are placing at the top of their must-have list when searching for the next move. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The trend?</strong> Smart homes. More specifically, smart home kitchens. </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.coldwellbanker.ca/press-release/smarthomes\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A study by Coldwell Banker Real Estate</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> found that 62 percent of agents are seeing more buyers interested in managing and controlling the technology in their home through a device - a smartphone or tablet - more than they were just two years ago. The United States leads the way in overall smart home adoption, with the estimated number of smart homes estimated to rise from 4.6 million to 24.5 million in just five years.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And kitchens? Smart kitchens and connected appliances are smarter, sleeker and greener than they ever have been. As an innovator, you owe it to yourself to stay ahead of your peers and give connected cooking a try, right? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Right. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you’re ready to take the leap into building your smart home kitchen, our top 10 must-have items are here. These products were selected by reviewing hundreds of product and review sites, taking the highest average review for each and every selection. Not only are they effective and innovative, they’re pushing the boundaries of the smart home and are prepared to make your kitchen greater than every before.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\">1. Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker</a></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-30\"><img class=\"wp-image-46 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/flmr-coffee-smart-coffee-maker0-700x394.jpg\" alt=\"mr coffee wifi coffee maker\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Because everyone needs a morning cup of coffee, right? We love this Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enable Coffeemaker. It\'s a high-quality coffeemaker that you can control with either your smartphone or your tablet, allowing you to set automated brewing schedules. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And the best part? You can receive push notifications when your coffee\'s ready, which makes your morning alarm so much easier.  </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Owners and reviewers alike are impressed by the Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker. Why? Scheduling and adjusting brew time and set-up reminders is a huge bonus, according to </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374411&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Mr.+Coffee%27s+WeMo-enabled+Smart\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reviewers on Amazon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“This machine has a lot of possibilities,” one reviewer said. “The one advantage this has is the Wemo app allows you to schedule one brew in your coffee maker each day of the week.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to the scheduler, this unit also brews coffee in under 7 minutes, and heats water to the optimal temperature. Manual operation is available (but who wouldn’t want to automate the brewing process?)  </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Egg-Minder-Wink-App-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00GN92KQ4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Egg Minder Wink App-Enabled Smart Egg Tray</span></a><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Egg-Minder-Wink-App-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00GN92KQ4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-47\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-47 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/banner_eggminder_blue-700x268.jpg\" alt=\"Egg Minder Wink App\" width=\"700\" height=\"268\" /></a></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You know when you’re just not quite sure if the eggs in your fridge are still in good shape to eat? This item will solve your morning grind. The Egg Minder was a Kickstarter success story. Not only will it keep count of your eggs, it will tell you which ones are the oldest and which ones are going bad. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Egg Minder Wink App-Enabled Smart Egg Tray Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers are in awe at this egg tray - and likely wonder why they hadn’t thought of it before. Although it’s such a simple product, reviewers love the in-tray LED lights that indicate the oldest egg, and the addition of push notifications that alert you when you\'re running low. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The best part? Amazon reviewers love that this device is  IFTTT compatible, so you can set up some great IoT combos. For example example, \"If I run out of eggs, play Hotline Bling on Spotify.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How great is that?</span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Scooba-Floor-Scrubbing-Robot/dp/B00IO9U06I/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. iRobot Scooba 450</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Scooba-Floor-Scrubbing-Robot/dp/B00IO9U06I/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-48\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-48\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/S450_PR-onstand-700x467.jpg\" alt=\"iRobot Scooba 450 Robot Vacuum\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although the iRobot Scooba 450 might look like a Roomba, it certainly isn’t. Spoiler alert: The Scooba does more than just vacuum. It uses a three-cycle process to soak, scrub and dry your floors, essentially replacing the mopping process. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>iRobot Scooba 450 Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/irobot-scooba-450/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers on CNET</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> have replaced their well-used cleaning accessories. Why? “iRobot\'s Scooba 450 really can replace your old mop and bucket. Separate tanks mean that dirty water doesn\'t get recycled back onto your floors”, which makes it a win/win for time and efficiency. </span>\r\n\r\nTwo room size options are available with this device - 150 square feet for 20 minutes of cleaning or 300 square feet for 40 minutes of cleaning, meaning you’ll find that this works for virtually any room in your home.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even better? Battery indicator lights ensure you’ll never run out of battery life. </span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">4. Anova Sous Vide</a></span></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-49\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-49\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/anova_sous_vide_thumbnail-700x525.jpg\" alt=\"anova_sous_vide_thumbnail\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sous Vide Precision cooking is a relatively new concept, but one that home cookers often swear by. Why? It’s essentially fool proof. Precision cookers make it easy to get professional results at home, circulating water around the pot while ensuring consistent temperatures throughout your ingredients. The best part is that the precision cooker also connects to your phone, allowing you to cook your meals with the touch of a button. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Anova Sous Vide Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Who wouldn’t want this? </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another time, I was working on a project and had just enough time to stop home for about 10 minutes. I bagged up some pork loin, tossed it in the stock pot filled with water, turned on the circulator, and headed back out for a couple hours. Came home, cooked some noodles and veggies and 15 mins later, had food ready to go. - </span></i><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/ref=sr_1_1?s=kitchen&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374965&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=anova\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon Review </span></i></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers love the Anova Sous Vide. It’s easy - offering a stainless steel skirt, which can be removed and cleaned in the dishwasher - and connected with your smartphone, as cooking notifications are sent as your meal is cooking, which allows you to monitor progress remotely </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Precision cooking holds food at a precise temperature so there is no worry about overcooking your meal. That sounds like a win for home chefs. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. First Alert OneLink</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-50\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-50\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/onelink-by-first-alert-with-app-2-HR-700x466.jpg\" alt=\"onelink-by-first-alert-with-app-2-HR\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every kitchen needs a smoke detector, and First Alert is making this as easy as ever. The entire suite of products from First Alert are all compatible with Apple\'s HomeKit system and can be controlled via iPhone. It’s a win/win, and a safety precaution. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>First Alert OneLink Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Safety and security are top of mind for reviewers online. Low battery warning and end of life timer make this product safe and secure, which is exactly what you need in your home connected kitchen. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wireless enabled, this battery operated detector creates a wireless safety network. The detector is also designed to provide you the earliest warning in an emergency, providing “peace of mind” according to </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reviewers on Amazon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Crock-Pot-SCCPWM600-V1-033-Enabled-Smart-Cooker/dp/B00TY7Q446/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6. Crock-Pot WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Crock-Pot-SCCPWM600-V1-033-Enabled-Smart-Cooker/dp/B00TY7Q446/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-51\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-51\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/SCCPWM600-V1-4-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"SCCPWM600-V1-4\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Similar to the Anova Sous Vide, this Crock Pot Smart Slow Cooker is seriously a lifesaver. This device connects via Wi-Fi and can be monitored and turned on and off using an iOS or Android mobile device, allowing you to control your dinner from the office. As well, you can also use an app to adjust temperature and timing on the fly, so if you’re getting home earlier than expected, you can easily adjust the speed well ahead of time. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“I did not know a slow cooker could be so high tech”, said </span><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">one reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We totally agree. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With remote access to all cooking functions, anywhere - and anytime - the Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker offers adjustable cooking time and temperature from your smart device, which is great for on-the-go home chefs. </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Wemo allowed me to remotely start and stop my meal, check how long it had been cooking and change the heat setting or turn it off.”</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> - </span><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crock-Pot.ca Review </span></a>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iDevices-IGR0001P5-iGrill-Mini-Thermometer/dp/B00I25PGZO/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">7. iGrill Mini</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iDevices-IGR0001P5-iGrill-Mini-Thermometer/dp/B00I25PGZO/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-53\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-53\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/71S9qPxtSoL._SL1500_-700x357.jpg\" alt=\"71S9qPxtSoL._SL1500_\" width=\"500\" height=\"255\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The iGrill Mini is a Bluetooth thermometer that allows you to check on the progress of your meal right from your smartphone. (We love smartphone enabled cooking devices, can’t you tell?) A companion app includes recommended cooking temperatures for just about every protein you can think of, which saves tons of time as you’re quickly whipping up your meal.  </span>\r\n\r\n<b>iGrill Mini Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The first thing I noticed about iGrill Mini is its diminutive size -- it measures just 2 inches by 2 inches,” </span><a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/idevices-igrill-mini/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">said one CNET reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. “It\'s just a cute, compact gadget with a lot of functionality packed into its small frame.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Online reviewers agree that it’s simple to set-up with smartphone devices, and promises to cook food without needing to check manually. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even better? You can select from among various presets categorized by temperature, making each and every recipe easier than the last. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">8. HAPIfork Bluetooth-Enabled Smart Fork</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-54\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-54\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/556680-1024x879-700x601.jpg\" alt=\"556680-1024x879\" width=\"500\" height=\"429\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A smart fork that helps you monitor and track your eating habits? It’s possible, and it’s here. This connected cutlery measures just how many mouthfuls you take during your meal, buzzing and flashing if you’re eating too quickly.  There’s also a great dashboard that lets you look back and analyzing your overall performance. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>HAPIfork Bluetooth-Enabled Smart Fork Reviews:\r\n</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Wow, what a great product! Before I owned a HAPIfork, I could never tell when I was eating too fast,” says this </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\nStatistics are available in real time, so you can review your analysis immediately. Een better? Set your workout objectives, track your progress and score points through the program.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And to share your results with friends? HAPI moments can be shared online, for your friends and followers to see. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">9. Prep Pad from the Orange Chef</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-55\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-55\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Orange-Chef-Cos-Smart-Food-Scale-The-Prep-Pad-1-700x467.jpg\" alt=\"Orange-Chef-Cos-Smart-Food-Scale-The-Prep-Pad-1\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prep Pad offers nutritional tracking with a twist. Tallying up nutritional info from the foods added to any bowl on its connected food scale, this product can tell you exactly how many carb, fat and protein calories are in your food. It truly makes meal prep so much easier.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Prep Pad from the Orange Chef Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The Prep Pad is easily one of my favorite tech + food products. Not only does it help me keep track of what I\'m eating, but it also helps me create a nutritional information sheet for my own recipes.” - </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon Reviewer</span></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Prep Pad gives you an overview of every ingredient you put on the food scale, allowing you to access a food library of more than 300,000 items. And like the Amazon reviewer said, you can track and log meals through your smartphone.</span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10. LG’s Smart Oven</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-56\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-56 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472.jpg\" alt=\"lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472\" width=\"630\" height=\"472\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We saved the biggest for last because we just needed to include LG’s smart oven in our list. This is truly the creme of the crop in the connected, smart kitchen. This connected kitchen appliance will allow you to gain control remotely from your smartphone. The best part? The accompanying app allows you to set it and (nearly) forget it - all while sending recipes to your range. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>LG’s Smart Oven Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The LG Smart Oven has left users “</span><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">totally satisfied with the range</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">”. With great features, including even cooking and a large oven, you can set precise temperature control remotely. The infrared grill system and the true convection oven have given this product a </span><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4.9 star review online</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The smart home kitchen is here - and it’s here to stay. With innovative and revolutionary products emerging from start-up organizations to large corporations alike, smart kitchen products are developing at a rapid rate. We’re excited to join this remarkable ride ahead.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','10 Must-Have Items for a Smart Home Kitchen','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-autosave-v1','','','2016-01-08 16:42:53','2016-01-08 16:42:53','',17,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/04/17-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(180,4,'2016-01-04 02:09:09','2016-01-04 02:09:09','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There’s a trend developing - and homeowners are starting to notice. What was once considered a benefit or luxury has now become the norm; a norm that buyers and agents alike are placing at the top of their must-have list when searching for the next move. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The trend?</strong> Smart homes. More specifically, smart home kitchens. </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.coldwellbanker.ca/press-release/smarthomes\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A study by Coldwell Banker Real Estate</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> found that 62 percent of agents are seeing more buyers interested in managing and controlling the technology in their home through a device - a smartphone or tablet - more than they were just two years ago. The United States leads the way in overall smart home adoption, with the estimated number of smart homes estimated to rise from 4.6 million to 24.5 million in just five years.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And kitchens? Smart kitchens and connected appliances are smarter, sleeker and greener than they ever have been. As an innovator, you owe it to yourself to stay ahead of your peers and give connected cooking a try, right? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Right. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you’re ready to take the leap into building your smart home kitchen, our top 10 must-have items are here. These products were selected by reviewing hundreds of product and review sites, taking the highest average review for each and every selection. Not only are they effective and innovative, they’re pushing the boundaries of the smart home and are prepared to make your kitchen greater than every before.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\">1. Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker</a></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_46\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"700\"]<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-30\"><img class=\"wp-image-46 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/flmr-coffee-smart-coffee-maker0-700x394.jpg\" alt=\"mr coffee wifi coffee maker\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" /></a> Mr Coffee WiFi Coffee[/caption]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Because everyone needs a morning cup of coffee, right? We love this Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enable Coffeemaker. It\'s a high-quality coffeemaker that you can control with either your smartphone or your tablet, allowing you to set automated brewing schedules. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And the best part? You can receive push notifications when your coffee\'s ready, which makes your morning alarm so much easier.  </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Owners and reviewers alike are impressed by the Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker. Why? Scheduling and adjusting brew time and set-up reminders is a huge bonus, according to </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374411&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Mr.+Coffee%27s+WeMo-enabled+Smart\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reviewers on Amazon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“This machine has a lot of possibilities,” one reviewer said. “The one advantage this has is the Wemo app allows you to schedule one brew in your coffee maker each day of the week.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to the scheduler, this unit also brews coffee in under 7 minutes, and heats water to the optimal temperature. Manual operation is available (but who wouldn’t want to automate the brewing process?)  </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Egg-Minder-Wink-App-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00GN92KQ4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Egg Minder Wink App-Enabled Smart Egg Tray</span></a><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Egg-Minder-Wink-App-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00GN92KQ4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-47\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-47 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/banner_eggminder_blue-700x268.jpg\" alt=\"Egg Minder Wink App\" width=\"700\" height=\"268\" /></a></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You know when you’re just not quite sure if the eggs in your fridge are still in good shape to eat? This item will solve your morning grind. The Egg Minder was a Kickstarter success story. Not only will it keep count of your eggs, it will tell you which ones are the oldest and which ones are going bad. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Egg Minder Wink App-Enabled Smart Egg Tray Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers are in awe at this egg tray - and likely wonder why they hadn’t thought of it before. Although it’s such a simple product, reviewers love the in-tray LED lights that indicate the oldest egg, and the addition of push notifications that alert you when you\'re running low. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The best part? Amazon reviewers love that this device is  IFTTT compatible, so you can set up some great IoT combos. For example example, \"If I run out of eggs, play Hotline Bling on Spotify.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How great is that?</span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/iRobot-Scooba-Floor-Scrubbing-Robot/dp/B00IO9U06I/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. iRobot Scooba 450</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/iRobot-Scooba-Floor-Scrubbing-Robot/dp/B00IO9U06I/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-48\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-48\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/S450_PR-onstand-700x467.jpg\" alt=\"iRobot Scooba 450 Robot Vacuum\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although the iRobot Scooba 450 might look like a Roomba, it certainly isn’t. Spoiler alert: The Scooba does more than just vacuum. It uses a three-cycle process to soak, scrub and dry your floors, essentially replacing the mopping process. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>iRobot Scooba 450 Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/irobot-scooba-450/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers on CNET</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> have replaced their well-used cleaning accessories. Why? “iRobot\'s Scooba 450 really can replace your old mop and bucket. Separate tanks mean that dirty water doesn\'t get recycled back onto your floors”, which makes it a win/win for time and efficiency. </span>\r\n\r\nTwo room size options are available with this device - 150 square feet for 20 minutes of cleaning or 300 square feet for 40 minutes of cleaning, meaning you’ll find that this works for virtually any room in your home.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even better? Battery indicator lights ensure you’ll never run out of battery life. </span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">4. Anova Sous Vide</a></span></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-49\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-49\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/anova_sous_vide_thumbnail-700x525.jpg\" alt=\"anova_sous_vide_thumbnail\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sous Vide Precision cooking is a relatively new concept, but one that home cookers often swear by. Why? It’s essentially fool proof. Precision cookers make it easy to get professional results at home, circulating water around the pot while ensuring consistent temperatures throughout your ingredients. The best part is that the precision cooker also connects to your phone, allowing you to cook your meals with the touch of a button. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Anova Sous Vide Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Who wouldn’t want this? </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another time, I was working on a project and had just enough time to stop home for about 10 minutes. I bagged up some pork loin, tossed it in the stock pot filled with water, turned on the circulator, and headed back out for a couple hours. Came home, cooked some noodles and veggies and 15 mins later, had food ready to go. - </span></i><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/ref=sr_1_1?s=kitchen&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374965&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=anova\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon Review </span></i></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers love the Anova Sous Vide. It’s easy - offering a stainless steel skirt, which can be removed and cleaned in the dishwasher - and connected with your smartphone, as cooking notifications are sent as your meal is cooking, which allows you to monitor progress remotely </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Precision cooking holds food at a precise temperature so there is no worry about overcooking your meal. That sounds like a win for home chefs. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. First Alert OneLink</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-50\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-50\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/onelink-by-first-alert-with-app-2-HR-700x466.jpg\" alt=\"onelink-by-first-alert-with-app-2-HR\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every kitchen needs a smoke detector, and First Alert is making this as easy as ever. The entire suite of products from First Alert are all compatible with Apple\'s HomeKit system and can be controlled via iPhone. It’s a win/win, and a safety precaution. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>First Alert OneLink Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Safety and security are top of mind for reviewers online. Low battery warning and end of life timer make this product safe and secure, which is exactly what you need in your home connected kitchen. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wireless enabled, this battery operated detector creates a wireless safety network. The detector is also designed to provide you the earliest warning in an emergency, providing “peace of mind” according to </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reviewers on Amazon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Crock-Pot-SCCPWM600-V1-033-Enabled-Smart-Cooker/dp/B00TY7Q446/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6. Crock-Pot WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Crock-Pot-SCCPWM600-V1-033-Enabled-Smart-Cooker/dp/B00TY7Q446/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-51\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-51\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/SCCPWM600-V1-4-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"SCCPWM600-V1-4\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Similar to the Anova Sous Vide, this Crock Pot Smart Slow Cooker is seriously a lifesaver. This device connects via Wi-Fi and can be monitored and turned on and off using an iOS or Android mobile device, allowing you to control your dinner from the office. As well, you can also use an app to adjust temperature and timing on the fly, so if you’re getting home earlier than expected, you can easily adjust the speed well ahead of time. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“I did not know a slow cooker could be so high tech”, said </span><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">one reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We totally agree. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With remote access to all cooking functions, anywhere - and anytime - the Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker offers adjustable cooking time and temperature from your smart device, which is great for on-the-go home chefs. </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Wemo allowed me to remotely start and stop my meal, check how long it had been cooking and change the heat setting or turn it off.”</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> - </span><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crock-Pot.ca Review </span></a>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/iDevices-IGR0001P5-iGrill-Mini-Thermometer/dp/B00I25PGZO/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">7. iGrill Mini</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/iDevices-IGR0001P5-iGrill-Mini-Thermometer/dp/B00I25PGZO/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-53\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-53\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/71S9qPxtSoL._SL1500_-700x357.jpg\" alt=\"71S9qPxtSoL._SL1500_\" width=\"500\" height=\"255\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The iGrill Mini is a Bluetooth thermometer that allows you to check on the progress of your meal right from your smartphone. (We love smartphone enabled cooking devices, can’t you tell?) A companion app includes recommended cooking temperatures for just about every protein you can think of, which saves tons of time as you’re quickly whipping up your meal.  </span>\r\n\r\n<b>iGrill Mini Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The first thing I noticed about iGrill Mini is its diminutive size -- it measures just 2 inches by 2 inches,” </span><a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/idevices-igrill-mini/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">said one CNET reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. “It\'s just a cute, compact gadget with a lot of functionality packed into its small frame.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Online reviewers agree that it’s simple to set-up with smartphone devices, and promises to cook food without needing to check manually. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even better? You can select from among various presets categorized by temperature, making each and every recipe easier than the last. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">8. HAPIfork Bluetooth-Enabled Smart Fork</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-54\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-54\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/556680-1024x879-700x601.jpg\" alt=\"556680-1024x879\" width=\"500\" height=\"429\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A smart fork that helps you monitor and track your eating habits? It’s possible, and it’s here. This connected cutlery measures just how many mouthfuls you take during your meal, buzzing and flashing if you’re eating too quickly.  There’s also a great dashboard that lets you look back and analyzing your overall performance. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>HAPIfork Bluetooth-Enabled Smart Fork Reviews:\r\n</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Wow, what a great product! Before I owned a HAPIfork, I could never tell when I was eating too fast,” says this </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\nStatistics are available in real time, so you can review your analysis immediately. Een better? Set your workout objectives, track your progress and score points through the program.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And to share your results with friends? HAPI moments can be shared online, for your friends and followers to see. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">9. Prep Pad from the Orange Chef</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-55\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-55\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Orange-Chef-Cos-Smart-Food-Scale-The-Prep-Pad-1-700x467.jpg\" alt=\"Orange-Chef-Cos-Smart-Food-Scale-The-Prep-Pad-1\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prep Pad offers nutritional tracking with a twist. Tallying up nutritional info from the foods added to any bowl on its connected food scale, this product can tell you exactly how many carb, fat and protein calories are in your food. It truly makes meal prep so much easier.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Prep Pad from the Orange Chef Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The Prep Pad is easily one of my favorite tech + food products. Not only does it help me keep track of what I\'m eating, but it also helps me create a nutritional information sheet for my own recipes.” - </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon Reviewer</span></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Prep Pad gives you an overview of every ingredient you put on the food scale, allowing you to access a food library of more than 300,000 items. And like the Amazon reviewer said, you can track and log meals through your smartphone.</span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10. LG’s Smart Oven</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-56\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-56 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472.jpg\" alt=\"lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472\" width=\"630\" height=\"472\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We saved the biggest for last because we just needed to include LG’s smart oven in our list. This is truly the creme of the crop in the connected, smart kitchen. This connected kitchen appliance will allow you to gain control remotely from your smartphone. The best part? The accompanying app allows you to set it and (nearly) forget it - all while sending recipes to your range. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>LG’s Smart Oven Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The LG Smart Oven has left users “</span><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">totally satisfied with the range</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">”. With great features, including even cooking and a large oven, you can set precise temperature control remotely. The infrared grill system and the true convection oven have given this product a </span><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4.9 star review online</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The smart home kitchen is here - and it’s here to stay. With innovative and revolutionary products emerging from start-up organizations to large corporations alike, smart kitchen products are developing at a rapid rate. We’re excited to join this remarkable ride ahead.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','10 Must-Have Items for a Smart Home Kitchen','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-revision-v1','','','2016-01-04 02:09:09','2016-01-04 02:09:09','',17,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/04/17-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(183,8,'2016-01-04 17:46:01','2016-01-04 17:46:01','','Hero-03','','inherit','open','closed','','hero-03','','','2016-01-04 17:46:01','2016-01-04 17:46:01','',136,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Hero-03.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),
	(184,9,'2016-01-04 19:50:27','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-01-04 19:50:27','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/?p=184',0,'post','',0),
	(185,7,'2016-01-04 21:42:25','2016-01-04 21:42:25','Bathrooms are notoriously expensive and labor-intensive to remodel when major renovations are involved. Once you start using words like <em>gut, repipe, </em>and <em>demo</em> you’re headed down a potentially long and costly road. In fact, <a href=\"http://www.remodeling.hw.net/benchmarks/cost-vs-value-nothing-average-here_o\">Remodeling Magazine recently reported</a> that the cost for an average bathroom remodel could range anywhere between $13,000 and a whopping $61,000. While a full remodel can add a lot of value to your home, we know that sometimes that isn’t in the budget.\r\n\r\nSo, what do you do when you’re craving a change to your en suite, but don’t have the time or budget for a total renovation? Scout products that can upgrade your space without having to hire a contractor or knock down any walls! By combining high quality décor items with some of the latest in smart home technology, you can create a whole new, exciting look and feel for your bathroom. You’ll be amazed what a few simple upgrades can do to make this space feel less like the family bathroom and more like a zen spa retreat.\r\n<h2><strong>We’ve compiled a list of nine awesome products which can give your bathroom a major facelift without having to do any major renovations.  </strong></h2>\r\nWe love a sleek and modern aesthetic, especially in a bathroom. We’ve chosen products for this list based on that style, and we’re pretty sure you’re going to love them as much as we do! While the following products range in price (anywhere from $50-$1,500) they all make a bold statement and provide a serious upgrade with minimal installation requirements.\r\n\r\nWe’ve also scouted some of the latest in smart home products, which are high-impact in a bathroom setting. Technology is allowing us to automate everything, including the temperature and pressure of our showers! In addition to these gadgets, this list includes a variety of sexy décor options which will add a sense of relaxation and beauty to your space.\r\n\r\nThe products on this list were selected because of their unique qualities and high-impact nature. Our choices were also based on great customer reviews from sites like Amazon.com and AllModern.com.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>1. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Moen-TS3420ORB-Digital-Vertical-Control/dp/B004SR3TOA/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449735904&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=moen+vertical+spa?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Moen Vertical Shower Spa</a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Moen-TS3420ORB-Digital-Vertical-Control/dp/B004SR3TOA/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449735904&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=moen+vertical+spa?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-103\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-113\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/moen-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"Moen TS3420ORB IO/Digital Vertical Spa Digital Control\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFor a smarter shower, this Moen system allows you to control not only the exact temperature of your water but also the pressure level and number of sprays. You can control your experience on this sleek wall-mounted device, which is an upgrade for your shower’s appearance as well as its quality.\r\n<h3>2. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Smart-Weigh-Precision-Technology-Backlight/dp/B00FJ8PI3M/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449390946&amp;sr=8-2&amp;keywords=smart+home+bathroom?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Smart Weigh Scale</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Smart-Weigh-Precision-Technology-Backlight/dp/B00FJ8PI3M/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449390946&amp;sr=8-2&amp;keywords=smart+home+bathroom?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-123\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-123\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/71ocZ1WeeTL._SL1500_-700x652.jpg\" alt=\"Smart Weigh Precision Digital Vanity / Bathroom Scale, &quot;Smart Step-On&quot; Technology, Tempered Glass Platform and Large Backlight Display\" width=\"500\" height=\"466\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThis lightweight glass scale boasts a modern look while incorporating smart technology. It can measure weight with incredible accuracy, helping you to manage your fitness without worrying about a faulty scale.\r\n<h3>3. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/561T-DST-Compel-Bathroom-Touch2O-Technology/dp/B00UOOBUTM/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449736745&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=Delta+smart+touch+bathroom?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Delta Bathroom Faucet Touch 2.0 </a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/561T-DST-Compel-Bathroom-Touch2O-Technology/dp/B00UOOBUTM/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449736745&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=Delta+smart+touch+bathroom?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-118\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-118\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/41X-pyr3PzL.jpg\" alt=\"Delta 561T-DST Compel Single Lever Handle Bathroom Faucet with Touch2O\" width=\"266\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\nUpgrading to a high-end faucet is a simple way to make a big impact in your bathroom. This one looks beautiful, and also adds that extra touch of tech to wow your guests. By simply touching any part of the faucet or waving your hands within 4 inches of it, water begins to flow.\r\n<h3>4. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/K-9245-CP-Showerhead-Wireless-Speaker-Polished/dp/B00A46X48A/ref=sr_1_31?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449392008&amp;sr=8-31&amp;keywords=shower+speaker+smart?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Showerhead with Speaker</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/K-9245-CP-Showerhead-Wireless-Speaker-Polished/dp/B00A46X48A/ref=sr_1_31?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449392008&amp;sr=8-31&amp;keywords=shower+speaker+smart?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-121\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-121\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/61cG2HhhniL._SL1317_-700x742.jpg\" alt=\"KOHLER K-9245-CP 2.5 GPM Moxie Showerhead and Wireless Speaker\" width=\"400\" height=\"424\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSo you love to sing in the shower, who doesn’t? Make your daily concerts sound <em>way </em>better with this Kohler showerhead. It includes a wireless speaker that syncs with Bluetooth-enabled devices, so you can play your favorite songs to your heart’s content. The speaker itself is also removable, and can be used in any other room of the house or on the go.\r\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Alessi-Birillo-Bathroom-Waste-Bin-PL10-W-AAS2740.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Bathroom Trashcan</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Alessi-Birillo-Bathroom-Waste-Bin-PL10-W-AAS2740.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-126\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-126\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/BirilloBathroomWasteBinbyPieroLissoni-2.jpg\" alt=\"Birillo Bathroom Waste Bin\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\nIn a room as small as a bathroom, each piece is important. This sleek, modern trashcan is a great finishing touch to your space. The simple-yet-functional design will blend seamlessly with your Smart House aesthetic.\r\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Oslo-Vanity-Bathroom-Mirror-with-Shelves-FHWA2432BK-DNB2001.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Bathroom Mirror with Shelves</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Oslo-Vanity-Bathroom-Mirror-with-Shelves-FHWA2432BK-DNB2001.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-128\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-128 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/DanyaBE284A2Oslo-24X31.522VanityBathroomMirrorwithShelves-Black-2.jpg\" alt=\"Oslo Vanity Bathroom Mirror with Shelves\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /></a>\r\n\r\nIf you’re not up for removing and replacing your entire bathroom vanity, swapping out the mirror above the one you have is a simple-but-impactful alternative. This one from All Modern also adds functionality with shelves.\r\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2-TXN1558.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Orchids Set</a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2-TXN1558.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-109\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-109 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2.jpg\" alt=\"Phaleanopsis Orchid with Black Vase Silk Flowers\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /></a>\r\n\r\nA few well-placed pieces of décor can add a lot to a small space. These faux orchids fit in with the modern, sexy vibe you’re looking for while adding a touch of softness to the space.\r\n<h3>8. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-ADAN1029.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Quote Candle</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-ADAN1029.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-130\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-130\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-2.jpg\" alt=\"Moroccan Ginger Jar Candle\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\nA candlelit bath is good for the soul, and this votive comes with an inspirational quote to help get you into a state of true zen.\r\n<h3>9. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Trademark-Fine-Art-Zen-Lotus-by-Kurt-Shaffer-Photographic-Print-on-Canvas-KS024-TMK4761.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Zen Wall Art</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Trademark-Fine-Art-Zen-Lotus-by-Kurt-Shaffer-Photographic-Print-on-Canvas-KS024-TMK4761.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-119\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-119 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/41ySX9dNJWL._SY355_-1.jpg\" alt=\"41ySX9dNJWL._SY355_\" width=\"355\" height=\"355\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFinally, when you don’t want to go through a major renovation, one of the simplest ways to upgrade a space is to add artwork to the walls. We love this romantic lotus print for an added sense of sexy sophistication.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith the addition of just a few products, you can change the look and feel of your bathroom drastically. It’s all about choosing a style and sticking with it, and knowing which pieces will give you the biggest bang for your buck. Luckily, in a bathroom setting figuring out which pieces to go with is fairly simple because it is such a small space. Consider which pieces are most functional within the space. For example, a nice trashcan in a larger room might not have as much impact as it would in the bathroom where its presence is functional as well as decorative.\r\n\r\nLikewise, upgrading the functionality of your space with the latest technology has a big impact in this room. You’ll use your shower and bathroom faucet on a daily basis, so upgrading them with cool tech features will be something you constantly get to enjoy.\r\n<h5><em>Have you recently upgraded your master bathroom? Have any experience with the products listed above, or a few of your own to add to our list? We’d love to hear about your adventures in “no renovations required” upgrades! </em></h5>','No Renovations Required: 9 Modern Products for a Smarter, Sexier Bathroom','','inherit','closed','closed','','90-revision-v1','','','2016-01-04 21:42:25','2016-01-04 21:42:25','',90,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/04/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(186,6,'2016-01-05 05:31:02','2016-01-05 05:31:02','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There’s a trend developing - and homeowners are starting to notice. What was once considered a benefit or luxury has now become the norm; a norm that buyers and agents alike are placing at the top of their must-have list when searching for the next move. </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>The trend?</strong> Smart homes. More specifically, smart home kitchens. </span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.coldwellbanker.ca/press-release/smarthomes\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A study by Coldwell Banker Real Estate</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> found that 62 percent of agents are seeing more buyers interested in managing and controlling the technology in their home through a device - a smartphone or tablet - more than they were just two years ago. The United States leads the way in overall smart home adoption, with the estimated number of smart homes estimated to rise from 4.6 million to 24.5 million in just five years.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And kitchens? Smart kitchens and connected appliances are smarter, sleeker and greener than they ever have been. As an innovator, you owe it to yourself to stay ahead of your peers and give connected cooking a try, right? </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Right. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you’re ready to take the leap into building your smart home kitchen, our top 10 must-have items are here. These products were selected by reviewing hundreds of product and review sites, taking the highest average review for each and every selection. Not only are they effective and innovative, they’re pushing the boundaries of the smart home and are prepared to make your kitchen greater than every before.</span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\">1. Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker</a></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> </span></h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_46\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"700\"]<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-30\"><img class=\"wp-image-46 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/flmr-coffee-smart-coffee-maker0-700x394.jpg\" alt=\"mr coffee wifi coffee maker\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" /></a> Mr Coffee WiFi Coffee[/caption]\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Because everyone needs a morning cup of coffee, right? We love this Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enable Coffeemaker. It\'s a high-quality coffeemaker that you can control with either your smartphone or your tablet, allowing you to set automated brewing schedules. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And the best part? You can receive push notifications when your coffee\'s ready, which makes your morning alarm so much easier.  </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Owners and reviewers alike are impressed by the Mr. Coffee Smart Wifi-Enabled Coffeemaker. Why? Scheduling and adjusting brew time and set-up reminders is a huge bonus, according to </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Mr-Coffee-Wifi-Enabled-Coffeemaker-BVMC-PSTX91WE/dp/B00LUFSSWG/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374411&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Mr.+Coffee%27s+WeMo-enabled+Smart\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reviewers on Amazon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“This machine has a lot of possibilities,” one reviewer said. “The one advantage this has is the Wemo app allows you to schedule one brew in your coffee maker each day of the week.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In addition to the scheduler, this unit also brews coffee in under 7 minutes, and heats water to the optimal temperature. Manual operation is available (but who wouldn’t want to automate the brewing process?)  </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Egg-Minder-Wink-App-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00GN92KQ4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. Egg Minder Wink App-Enabled Smart Egg Tray</span></a><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Egg-Minder-Wink-App-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00GN92KQ4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-47\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-47 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/banner_eggminder_blue-700x268.jpg\" alt=\"Egg Minder Wink App\" width=\"700\" height=\"268\" /></a></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You know when you’re just not quite sure if the eggs in your fridge are still in good shape to eat? This item will solve your morning grind. The Egg Minder was a Kickstarter success story. Not only will it keep count of your eggs, it will tell you which ones are the oldest and which ones are going bad. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Egg Minder Wink App-Enabled Smart Egg Tray Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers are in awe at this egg tray - and likely wonder why they hadn’t thought of it before. Although it’s such a simple product, reviewers love the in-tray LED lights that indicate the oldest egg, and the addition of push notifications that alert you when you\'re running low. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The best part? Amazon reviewers love that this device is  IFTTT compatible, so you can set up some great IoT combos. For example example, \"If I run out of eggs, play Hotline Bling on Spotify.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How great is that?</span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Scooba-Floor-Scrubbing-Robot/dp/B00IO9U06I/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. iRobot Scooba 450</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Scooba-Floor-Scrubbing-Robot/dp/B00IO9U06I/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-48\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-48\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/S450_PR-onstand-700x467.jpg\" alt=\"iRobot Scooba 450 Robot Vacuum\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although the iRobot Scooba 450 might look like a Roomba, it certainly isn’t. Spoiler alert: The Scooba does more than just vacuum. It uses a three-cycle process to soak, scrub and dry your floors, essentially replacing the mopping process. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>iRobot Scooba 450 Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/irobot-scooba-450/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers on CNET</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> have replaced their well-used cleaning accessories. Why? “iRobot\'s Scooba 450 really can replace your old mop and bucket. Separate tanks mean that dirty water doesn\'t get recycled back onto your floors”, which makes it a win/win for time and efficiency. </span>\r\n\r\nTwo room size options are available with this device - 150 square feet for 20 minutes of cleaning or 300 square feet for 40 minutes of cleaning, meaning you’ll find that this works for virtually any room in your home.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even better? Battery indicator lights ensure you’ll never run out of battery life. </span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">4. Anova Sous Vide</a></span></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-49\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-49\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/anova_sous_vide_thumbnail-700x525.jpg\" alt=\"anova_sous_vide_thumbnail\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sous Vide Precision cooking is a relatively new concept, but one that home cookers often swear by. Why? It’s essentially fool proof. Precision cookers make it easy to get professional results at home, circulating water around the pot while ensuring consistent temperatures throughout your ingredients. The best part is that the precision cooker also connects to your phone, allowing you to cook your meals with the touch of a button. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Anova Sous Vide Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Who wouldn’t want this? </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another time, I was working on a project and had just enough time to stop home for about 10 minutes. I bagged up some pork loin, tossed it in the stock pot filled with water, turned on the circulator, and headed back out for a couple hours. Came home, cooked some noodles and veggies and 15 mins later, had food ready to go. - </span></i><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/Anova-Culinary-Precision-Immersion-Circulator/dp/B00UKPBXM4/ref=sr_1_1?s=kitchen&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450374965&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=anova\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon Review </span></i></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Reviewers love the Anova Sous Vide. It’s easy - offering a stainless steel skirt, which can be removed and cleaned in the dishwasher - and connected with your smartphone, as cooking notifications are sent as your meal is cooking, which allows you to monitor progress remotely </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Precision cooking holds food at a precise temperature so there is no worry about overcooking your meal. That sounds like a win for home chefs. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. First Alert OneLink</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-50\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-50\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/onelink-by-first-alert-with-app-2-HR-700x466.jpg\" alt=\"onelink-by-first-alert-with-app-2-HR\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every kitchen needs a smoke detector, and First Alert is making this as easy as ever. The entire suite of products from First Alert are all compatible with Apple\'s HomeKit system and can be controlled via iPhone. It’s a win/win, and a safety precaution. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>First Alert OneLink Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Safety and security are top of mind for reviewers online. Low battery warning and end of life timer make this product safe and secure, which is exactly what you need in your home connected kitchen. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Wireless enabled, this battery operated detector creates a wireless safety network. The detector is also designed to provide you the earliest warning in an emergency, providing “peace of mind” according to </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/First-Alert-SCO501CN-3ST-Interconnected-Combination/dp/B000EVO7C2\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reviewers on Amazon</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Crock-Pot-SCCPWM600-V1-033-Enabled-Smart-Cooker/dp/B00TY7Q446/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6. Crock-Pot WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Crock-Pot-SCCPWM600-V1-033-Enabled-Smart-Cooker/dp/B00TY7Q446/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-51\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-51\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/SCCPWM600-V1-4-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"SCCPWM600-V1-4\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Similar to the Anova Sous Vide, this Crock Pot Smart Slow Cooker is seriously a lifesaver. This device connects via Wi-Fi and can be monitored and turned on and off using an iOS or Android mobile device, allowing you to control your dinner from the office. As well, you can also use an app to adjust temperature and timing on the fly, so if you’re getting home earlier than expected, you can easily adjust the speed well ahead of time. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“I did not know a slow cooker could be so high tech”, said </span><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">one reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We totally agree. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With remote access to all cooking functions, anywhere - and anytime - the Crock-Pot® WeMo® Enabled Smart Slow Cooker offers adjustable cooking time and temperature from your smart device, which is great for on-the-go home chefs. </span>\r\n\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Wemo allowed me to remotely start and stop my meal, check how long it had been cooking and change the heat setting or turn it off.”</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> - </span><a href=\"http://www.crock-pot.ca/en_CA/slow-cookers/crock-pot-wemo-enabled-smart-slow-cooker/SCCPWM600-V1.html#q=smart&amp;start=1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Crock-Pot.ca Review </span></a>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iDevices-IGR0001P5-iGrill-Mini-Thermometer/dp/B00I25PGZO/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">7. iGrill Mini</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iDevices-IGR0001P5-iGrill-Mini-Thermometer/dp/B00I25PGZO/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-53\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-53\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/71S9qPxtSoL._SL1500_-700x357.jpg\" alt=\"71S9qPxtSoL._SL1500_\" width=\"500\" height=\"255\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The iGrill Mini is a Bluetooth thermometer that allows you to check on the progress of your meal right from your smartphone. (We love smartphone enabled cooking devices, can’t you tell?) A companion app includes recommended cooking temperatures for just about every protein you can think of, which saves tons of time as you’re quickly whipping up your meal.  </span>\r\n\r\n<b>iGrill Mini Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The first thing I noticed about iGrill Mini is its diminutive size -- it measures just 2 inches by 2 inches,” </span><a href=\"http://www.cnet.com/products/idevices-igrill-mini/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">said one CNET reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. “It\'s just a cute, compact gadget with a lot of functionality packed into its small frame.” </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Online reviewers agree that it’s simple to set-up with smartphone devices, and promises to cook food without needing to check manually. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Even better? You can select from among various presets categorized by temperature, making each and every recipe easier than the last. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">8. HAPIfork Bluetooth-Enabled Smart Fork</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-54\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-54\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/556680-1024x879-700x601.jpg\" alt=\"556680-1024x879\" width=\"500\" height=\"429\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A smart fork that helps you monitor and track your eating habits? It’s possible, and it’s here. This connected cutlery measures just how many mouthfuls you take during your meal, buzzing and flashing if you’re eating too quickly.  There’s also a great dashboard that lets you look back and analyzing your overall performance. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>HAPIfork Bluetooth-Enabled Smart Fork Reviews:\r\n</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Wow, what a great product! Before I owned a HAPIfork, I could never tell when I was eating too fast,” says this </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Hapilabs-102-HAPIfork-Bluetooth-Enabled-Smart/dp/B00FRPCPEC/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon reviewer</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\nStatistics are available in real time, so you can review your analysis immediately. Een better? Set your workout objectives, track your progress and score points through the program.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And to share your results with friends? HAPI moments can be shared online, for your friends and followers to see. </span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">9. Prep Pad from the Orange Chef</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-55\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-55\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Orange-Chef-Cos-Smart-Food-Scale-The-Prep-Pad-1-700x467.jpg\" alt=\"Orange-Chef-Cos-Smart-Food-Scale-The-Prep-Pad-1\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prep Pad offers nutritional tracking with a twist. Tallying up nutritional info from the foods added to any bowl on its connected food scale, this product can tell you exactly how many carb, fat and protein calories are in your food. It truly makes meal prep so much easier.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Prep Pad from the Orange Chef Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The Prep Pad is easily one of my favorite tech + food products. Not only does it help me keep track of what I\'m eating, but it also helps me create a nutritional information sheet for my own recipes.” - </span><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/The-Orange-Chef-Smart-Silver/dp/B00KFW8L90\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Amazon Reviewer</span></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The Prep Pad gives you an overview of every ingredient you put on the food scale, allowing you to access a food library of more than 300,000 items. And like the Amazon reviewer said, you can track and log meals through your smartphone.</span>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10. LG’s Smart Oven</span></a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-56\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-56 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472.jpg\" alt=\"lg-smart-washer-dryer-630x472\" width=\"630\" height=\"472\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We saved the biggest for last because we just needed to include LG’s smart oven in our list. This is truly the creme of the crop in the connected, smart kitchen. This connected kitchen appliance will allow you to gain control remotely from your smartphone. The best part? The accompanying app allows you to set it and (nearly) forget it - all while sending recipes to your range. </span>\r\n\r\n<b>LG’s Smart Oven Reviews:</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The LG Smart Oven has left users “</span><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">totally satisfied with the range</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">”. With great features, including even cooking and a large oven, you can set precise temperature control remotely. The infrared grill system and the true convection oven have given this product a </span><a href=\"http://www.lg.com/us/cooking-appliances/lg-LRE3027ST-electric-range\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4.9 star review online</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The smart home kitchen is here - and it’s here to stay. With innovative and revolutionary products emerging from start-up organizations to large corporations alike, smart kitchen products are developing at a rapid rate. We’re excited to join this remarkable ride ahead.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','10 Must-Have Items for a Smart Home Kitchen','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-revision-v1','','','2016-01-05 05:31:02','2016-01-05 05:31:02','',17,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/05/17-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(187,6,'2016-01-05 05:32:30','2016-01-05 05:32:30','Smart home door locks are arguably one of the most comforting items you can have in your home. Not only can they automatically detect your presence and provide safety while you\'re away, they can also send electronic keys to friends and family that will only work during specified hours, allowing you to let just about anyone you trust into your home while you\'re unable to answer the door.\n\n<strong>Isn\'t that so much better than your traditional, conventional key locks? </strong>\n\nIf you\'re considering purchasing a smart home door lock as your next purchase, you should certainly know your options. With so many products on the market, from price points to feature sets, be sure to explore the best option for you.\n\nWe\'ve put together the five best smart home locks based on price point, <strong>with all locks being under $300</strong>. To not spoil the surprise, we\'re counting down from #5, all the way through to the top spot.\n\nRead on.\n<h1></h1>\n<h3><strong>5. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Lockitron-Keyless-Entry-Using-Phone/dp/B00L3WUUMW/ref=cm_cr_pr_product_top?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Lockitron</a></strong></h3>\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Lockitron-Keyless-Entry-Using-Phone/dp/B00L3WUUMW/ref=cm_cr_pr_product_top?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.wareable.com/media/images/2015/07/1-lockitron-1436375698-Hyk1-full-width-inline.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></a>\n\nLockitron\'s \'The Bolt\' is the second generation product from the brand. The Bolt has learned from previous bugs in their product, and has released a new and improved smart home lock innovation. This product works wirelessly with both Buetooth and Wi-Fi, which means that users have two options in the opening experience, plus the ability to lock or unlock your home for anyone - be it friends, family or a parcel delivery.\n\n<a style=\"line-height: 1.5;\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Lockitron-Keyless-Entry-Using-Phone/dp/B00L3WUUMW/ref=cm_cr_pr_product_top?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\n<blockquote><em>\"Bluetooth 4.0 is always on and detects your device when you approach it and have the Lockitron App open on your phone\"</em>\n\n<em>“It can sense if your door has been unlocked, dutifully notifying you immediately.”</em>\n\n<em>“ You can pay for your coffee, turn off your lights, control your TV, and start your car with your smartphone — so why can\'t you unlock your doors? That\'s exactly what Lockitron does. ”</em></blockquote>\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\n\nThe big sell for us is the price point. This smart lock runs around $99 which, for the features available, is impressive. We love that \"The Bolt\" has all of the options available from the \'big guys\' - unlocking your home from anywhere in the world, email notifications when batteries are running low and super easy installation. It\'s a great smart home lock to try on your own.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><strong>4. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/OKIDOKEYS-SMART-LOCK-Bluetooth-Smartphone-Compatible/dp/B00IVKGF3C/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">OKIDOKEYS Classic</a></strong></h3>\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/OKIDOKEYS-SMART-LOCK-Bluetooth-Smartphone-Compatible/dp/B00IVKGF3C/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://cdn.toptenreviews.com/rev/prod/large/60621-okidokeys-smart-lock-box.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\n\nWith the OKIDOKEY Classic, your phone becomes your key, working with multiple Android and iOS phones. The product promises easy installation in just a \"few minutes\", with no drilling required. From creating a key for your babysitter to defining specific entry times for mail delivery, the OKIDOKEY Classic provides safe, easy access to your home.\n\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/OKIDOKEYS-SMART-LOCK-Bluetooth-Smartphone-Compatible/dp/B00IVKGF3C/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\n<blockquote><em>\"I\'ve loved my experience with Okidokeys locks (I got 2 access packs). Installing was as I would expect, I pulled it out and starting slapping it together, when I had a problem I read the directions and watched the install video. Magic, it worked.\"</em>\n\n<em>\"This is an absolutely BRILLIANT product!\"</em>\n\n<em>\"I installed the Smart Lock yesterday. It took me about 5 minutes to install after I read thru everything first. It works great for my family.\"</em></blockquote>\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\n\nOKIDOKEYS offers 6 opening rules to fit your needs, which is something that stood out to us. Among these opening rules is a hands-free mode that unlocks the door automatically when you are close to it (think of the auto-opening door that Tesla offers). The best part? This lock features a built-in alarm that notifies you when an intruder, or someone you\'re not expecting, attempts to enter your door. We love the safety and security this lock offers.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><strong>3. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Danalock-Integrated-Smartlock-Bluetooth-Compatible/dp/B00K4HRQBK/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Danalock</a></strong></h3>\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Danalock-Integrated-Smartlock-Bluetooth-Compatible/dp/B00K4HRQBK/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://www.wareable.com/media/images/2015/07/1-danalock-1436375710-eE7i-full-width-inline.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" /></a></h3>\nThe Danalock from Denmark promises great design for both the product and the app, something that home owners are always searching for when finding a smart home lock. Rest assured, although this product is from Denmark, it does come in SKUs to fit all sorts of European and North American doors with wireless and connectivity standards to match. The product promises patented, highest level of encrypted security available.\n\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Danalock-Integrated-Smartlock-Bluetooth-Compatible/dp/B00K4HRQBK/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\n<blockquote><em>\"The Danalock is beautifully designed, and looks on the outside much like the August smart lock.\"</em>\n\n<em>\"This was a cinch to install. I got mine installed in about 20 minutes after I read the instructions and downloaded the app.\"</em>\n\n<em>\"It was not at all complicated to install. The instructions were very clear. I am very excited about this product!\"</em></blockquote>\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\n\nWe love the design of this product. The Danalock has not fallen short in any capacity throughout the design and technology process. It also looks incredibly easy - all you need to do is supply the orders to your lock directly from your smartphone or computer, and schedule entry for yourself or others. According to reviews online, installation is straight-forward, with great support available.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><strong>2. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Kwikset-Cylinder-Bluetooth-Enabled-Deadbolt/dp/B00CPTD5AQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Kwikset Kevo</a></strong></h3>\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Kwikset-Cylinder-Bluetooth-Enabled-Deadbolt/dp/B00CPTD5AQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://www.wareable.com/media/images/2015/07/2-kevo-spl2-1436376090-nXGp-full-width-inline.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"905\" height=\"510\" /></a>\n\nThe Kwikset Kevo is just about the gold standard on the market. Not only has it been around for a significant period of time, but it also has some big pluses - like self-install, free, unlimited guest eKeys, and a lengthy history of notifications to tell you who as entered. The Kwikset Kevo allows you to leave your smartphone in your pocket or purse upon entering your, making sure you\'ll never have to fumble for keys again.  Convenient, isn\'t it?\n\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Kwikset-Cylinder-Bluetooth-Enabled-Deadbolt/dp/B00CPTD5AQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\n<blockquote><em>\"This product has saved my bacon many times, especially when carrying something heavy/cumbersome. I cannot tell you how integrated this lock is my daily routine. \"</em>\n\n<em>\"Installation and setup was quick and pretty painless. We rekeyed both new locks with our existing Kwikset key.\"</em>\n\n<em>\"The installation instructions were flawless, and all the hardware needed was present. The only tool you need is a screwdriver.\"</em></blockquote>\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\n\nThe Kwikset Kevo has been on the market for a lengthy period of time, meaning that many of the natural bugs in smart home locks have already been worked through. The greatest bonus that we love is that this lock looks fairly normal from the outside - it\'s a definite bonus, as it\'s not a distraction to passerby\'s or neighbors. The Kwikset is also coming out with the Kwikset Plus, giving you greater control over your home - like the ability to respond to emergencies by giving a neighbor access to your home, knowing when home service providers enter and leave and never wondering when your door is locked or unlocked.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><strong>1. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/August-AUG-SL01-M01-G01-electronic-keyless-access/dp/B00QI6FVIQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">August Smart Lock</a></strong></h3>\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/August-AUG-SL01-M01-G01-electronic-keyless-access/dp/B00QI6FVIQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/61VmYxoWcnL._SL1000_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" /></a></strong>\nWith over 140 reviews on Amazon alone, the August Smart Lock is one of the most popular locks in this price range. The August Smart Lock allows you to lock and unlock your door, create virtual keys for family and friends and keep a close eye on who comes and goes. A 24/7 activity log (available on your smartphone) tracks who enters and exits your home, so you’ll always know who opens your door and when.\n\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.ca/August-AUG-SL01-M01-G01-electronic-keyless-access/dp/B00QI6FVIQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\n<blockquote><em>\"Good looks, strong user management, and convenient automated features make the August Smart Lock a leader in its niche.\"</em>\n\n<em>\"The August app allows you to easily lock or unlock August Smart Lock with a single tap once you’ve selected the lock—It allows you to add and add multiple locks. The user interface is well designed and makes using the app a pleasant experience.\"</em>\n\n<em>\"Installation was simple with the included instructions and took under twenty minutes. Simple and easy.\"</em></blockquote>\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\n\nThe asking price puts August on the more expensive side of the smart lock spectrum, but the reviewers aren\'t lying. This product is extremely easy to connect, as your exterior door hardware stays the same. There is nothing to wire or connect. When batteries need replacing, you’ll be notified by the app. In addition, August Smart Lock has also recently released the August Smart Lock HomeKit Enabled edition, meaning that your smartphone is now a smart key-and more; it utilizes Siri, and gives you the ability to know who is entering your home - and when. This product syncs with <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/August-AC-R2-Connect/dp/B0168IXNFQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">August Connect</a> so you can unlock the door from anywhere in the world via the Internet.\n<h3>In conclusion...</h3>\nSmart home door locks are emerging on the market quicker than ever, which means greater competition in the marketplace. With so many options available, we are sure there will be new, innovative products in months to come. These five smart home door locks under $300 are great options for your home that will provide safety, security and ease for yourself and your visitors.','5 Best Smart Home Locks','','inherit','closed','closed','','136-autosave-v1','','','2016-01-05 05:32:30','2016-01-05 05:32:30','',136,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/05/136-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
