	(191,4,'2016-01-07 17:11:33','2016-01-07 17:11:33','Bathrooms are notoriously expensive and labor-intensive to remodel when major renovations are involved. Once you start using words like <em>gut, repipe, </em>and <em>demo</em> you’re headed down a potentially long and costly road. In fact, <a href=\"http://www.remodeling.hw.net/benchmarks/cost-vs-value-nothing-average-here_o\">Remodeling Magazine recently reported</a> that the cost for an average bathroom remodel could range anywhere between $13,000 and a whopping $61,000. While a full remodel can add a lot of value to your home, we know that sometimes that isn’t in the budget.\r\n\r\nSo, what do you do when you’re craving a change to your en suite, but don’t have the time or budget for a total renovation? Scout products that can upgrade your space without having to hire a contractor or knock down any walls! By combining high quality décor items with some of the latest in smart home technology, you can create a whole new, exciting look and feel for your bathroom. You’ll be amazed what a few simple upgrades can do to make this space feel less like the family bathroom and more like a zen spa retreat.\r\n<h2><strong>We’ve compiled a list of nine awesome products which can give your bathroom a major facelift without having to do any major renovations.  </strong></h2>\r\nWe love a sleek and modern aesthetic, especially in a bathroom. We’ve chosen products for this list based on that style, and we’re pretty sure you’re going to love them as much as we do! While the following products range in price (anywhere from $50-$1,500) they all make a bold statement and provide a serious upgrade with minimal installation requirements.\r\n\r\nWe’ve also scouted some of the latest in smart home products, which are high-impact in a bathroom setting. Technology is allowing us to automate everything, including the temperature and pressure of our showers! In addition to these gadgets, this list includes a variety of sexy décor options which will add a sense of relaxation and beauty to your space.\r\n\r\nThe products on this list were selected because of their unique qualities and high-impact nature. Our choices were also based on great customer reviews from sites like Amazon.com and AllModern.com.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>1. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Moen-TS3420ORB-Digital-Vertical-Control/dp/B004SR3TOA/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449735904&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=moen+vertical+spa?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Moen Vertical Shower Spa</a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Moen-TS3420ORB-Digital-Vertical-Control/dp/B004SR3TOA/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449735904&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=moen+vertical+spa?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-103\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-113\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/moen-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"Moen TS3420ORB IO/Digital Vertical Spa Digital Control\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFor a smarter shower, this Moen system allows you to control not only the exact temperature of your water but also the pressure level and number of sprays. You can control your experience on this sleek wall-mounted device, which is an upgrade for your shower’s appearance as well as its quality.\r\n<h3>2. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Smart-Weigh-Precision-Technology-Backlight/dp/B00FJ8PI3M/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449390946&amp;sr=8-2&amp;keywords=smart+home+bathroom?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Smart Weigh Scale</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Smart-Weigh-Precision-Technology-Backlight/dp/B00FJ8PI3M/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449390946&amp;sr=8-2&amp;keywords=smart+home+bathroom?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-123\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-123\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/71ocZ1WeeTL._SL1500_-700x652.jpg\" alt=\"Smart Weigh Precision Digital Vanity / Bathroom Scale, &quot;Smart Step-On&quot; Technology, Tempered Glass Platform and Large Backlight Display\" width=\"500\" height=\"466\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThis lightweight glass scale boasts a modern look while incorporating smart technology. It can measure weight with incredible accuracy, helping you to manage your fitness without worrying about a faulty scale.\r\n<h3>3. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/561T-DST-Compel-Bathroom-Touch2O-Technology/dp/B00UOOBUTM/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449736745&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=Delta+smart+touch+bathroom?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Delta Bathroom Faucet Touch 2.0 </a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/561T-DST-Compel-Bathroom-Touch2O-Technology/dp/B00UOOBUTM/ref=sr_1_3?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449736745&amp;sr=8-3&amp;keywords=Delta+smart+touch+bathroom?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-118\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-118\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/41X-pyr3PzL.jpg\" alt=\"Delta 561T-DST Compel Single Lever Handle Bathroom Faucet with Touch2O\" width=\"266\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\nUpgrading to a high-end faucet is a simple way to make a big impact in your bathroom. This one looks beautiful, and also adds that extra touch of tech to wow your guests. By simply touching any part of the faucet or waving your hands within 4 inches of it, water begins to flow.\r\n<h3>4. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/K-9245-CP-Showerhead-Wireless-Speaker-Polished/dp/B00A46X48A/ref=sr_1_31?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449392008&amp;sr=8-31&amp;keywords=shower+speaker+smart?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Showerhead with Speaker</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/K-9245-CP-Showerhead-Wireless-Speaker-Polished/dp/B00A46X48A/ref=sr_1_31?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1449392008&amp;sr=8-31&amp;keywords=shower+speaker+smart?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-121\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-121\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/61cG2HhhniL._SL1317_-700x742.jpg\" alt=\"KOHLER K-9245-CP 2.5 GPM Moxie Showerhead and Wireless Speaker\" width=\"400\" height=\"424\" /></a>\r\n\r\nSo you love to sing in the shower, who doesn’t? Make your daily concerts sound <em>way </em>better with this Kohler showerhead. It includes a wireless speaker that syncs with Bluetooth-enabled devices, so you can play your favorite songs to your heart’s content. The speaker itself is also removable, and can be used in any other room of the house or on the go.\r\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Alessi-Birillo-Bathroom-Waste-Bin-PL10-W-AAS2740.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Bathroom Trashcan</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Alessi-Birillo-Bathroom-Waste-Bin-PL10-W-AAS2740.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-126\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-126\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/BirilloBathroomWasteBinbyPieroLissoni-2.jpg\" alt=\"Birillo Bathroom Waste Bin\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\nIn a room as small as a bathroom, each piece is important. This sleek, modern trashcan is a great finishing touch to your space. The simple-yet-functional design will blend seamlessly with your Smart House aesthetic.\r\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Oslo-Vanity-Bathroom-Mirror-with-Shelves-FHWA2432BK-DNB2001.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Bathroom Mirror with Shelves</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Oslo-Vanity-Bathroom-Mirror-with-Shelves-FHWA2432BK-DNB2001.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-128\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-128 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/DanyaBE284A2Oslo-24X31.522VanityBathroomMirrorwithShelves-Black-2.jpg\" alt=\"Oslo Vanity Bathroom Mirror with Shelves\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /></a>\r\n\r\nIf you’re not up for removing and replacing your entire bathroom vanity, swapping out the mirror above the one you have is a simple-but-impactful alternative. This one from All Modern also adds functionality with shelves.\r\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2-TXN1558.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Orchids Set</a></h3>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2-TXN1558.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-109\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-109 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Nearly-Natural-Phaleanopsis-Orchid-with-Black-Vase-Silk-Arrangement-4757-S2.jpg\" alt=\"Phaleanopsis Orchid with Black Vase Silk Flowers\" width=\"525\" height=\"525\" /></a>\r\n\r\nA few well-placed pieces of décor can add a lot to a small space. These faux orchids fit in with the modern, sexy vibe you’re looking for while adding a touch of softness to the space.\r\n<h3>8. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-ADAN1029.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Quote Candle</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-ADAN1029.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-130\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-130\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Expression-Moroccan-Ginger-Votive-Candle-5103-2.jpg\" alt=\"Moroccan Ginger Jar Candle\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" /></a>\r\n\r\nA candlelit bath is good for the soul, and this votive comes with an inspirational quote to help get you into a state of true zen.\r\n<h3>9. <a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Trademark-Fine-Art-Zen-Lotus-by-Kurt-Shaffer-Photographic-Print-on-Canvas-KS024-TMK4761.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Zen Wall Art</a></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.allmodern.com/Trademark-Fine-Art-Zen-Lotus-by-Kurt-Shaffer-Photographic-Print-on-Canvas-KS024-TMK4761.html?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-119\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-119 size-full\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/41ySX9dNJWL._SY355_-1.jpg\" alt=\"41ySX9dNJWL._SY355_\" width=\"355\" height=\"355\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFinally, when you don’t want to go through a major renovation, one of the simplest ways to upgrade a space is to add artwork to the walls. We love this romantic lotus print for an added sense of sexy sophistication.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWith the addition of just a few products, you can change the look and feel of your bathroom drastically. It’s all about choosing a style and sticking with it, and knowing which pieces will give you the biggest bang for your buck. Luckily, in a bathroom setting figuring out which pieces to go with is fairly simple because it is such a small space. Consider which pieces are most functional within the space. For example, a nice trashcan in a larger room might not have as much impact as it would in the bathroom where its presence is functional as well as decorative.\r\n\r\nLikewise, upgrading the functionality of your space with the latest technology has a big impact in this room. You’ll use your shower and bathroom faucet on a daily basis, so upgrading them with cool tech features will be something you constantly get to enjoy.\r\n<h5><em>Have you recently upgraded your master bathroom? Have any experience with the products listed above, or a few of your own to add to our list? We’d love to hear about your adventures in “no renovations required” upgrades! </em></h5>','No Renovations: 9 Modern Products for a Smarter &  Sexier Bathroom','','inherit','closed','closed','','90-revision-v1','','','2016-01-07 17:11:33','2016-01-07 17:11:33','',90,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/07/90-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(192,4,'2016-01-07 19:21:37','2016-01-07 19:21:37','','Smart Door Locks','','inherit','open','closed','','hero-door','','','2016-01-07 19:21:50','2016-01-07 19:21:50','',136,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/hero-door.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),
	(194,6,'2016-01-08 03:31:50','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Just like <a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/04/best-smart-home-locks/\" target=\"_blank\">door locks</a>, phones and watches, light bulbs have become significantly more sophisticated over the last few years.\r\n\r\n<em>(If you told your Grandparent that you\'re able to control the light bulb in your home office from your smart phone, what would they say?)</em>\r\n\r\nYour standard light bulb is now being replaced by a number of home connected lighting solutions - solutions that you <strong>can</strong> control with just a few taps on your smart phone device. But with this new advent of connectivity, there are just so many options flooding the market. From disparity in pricing to various feature sets, it can often be hard to determine the best product for your home.\r\n\r\nTo help you make the best decision for your lifestyle, we\'ve compiled five of the best smart light bulbs that we\'ve found. These recommendations are based off research and customer reviews from Amazon, PCMag, WayFair and more.\r\n\r\n<em>Note: Our recommendations are in no particular order. </em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>1. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/LIFX-White-Adjustable-Dimmable-Required/dp/B00XUW0ZFU/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">LIFX White 800 LED Light Bulb</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/LIFX-White-Adjustable-Dimmable-Required/dp/B00XUW0ZFU/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/61D0xHYIesL._SL1250_.jpg\" alt=\"LIFX White Adjustable Light Bulb\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1250\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe LIFX White 800 LED is a bulb that you can control from your smart phone device. This product gives you the ability to personalize your environment, from setting a cool white light during the day or opting for a rich warm glow as you enter the evening. This solution connects to Wi-Fi, and all technology is built within each bulb.  All settings can be adjusted from the app, which is compatible for your smart phone and tablet.\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/LIFX-White-Adjustable-Dimmable-Required/dp/B00XUW0ZFU/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">What Amazon users are saying...</a></strong>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"Setup was much easier than I had expected and the LIFX app was well thought out. You can change the name of each bulb, create groups to control simultaneously, or control each bulb individually!\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>“We have over a dozen in the house and we use them for several different areas. Kids room for fun colors.”</em>\r\n\r\n<em>“Setup could not be more simple. The light is perfect 60watt equiv. brightness. The color temperature can be adjusted which is awesome.”</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nFrom all accounts, this bulb is nearly perfect. It doesn\'t require a hub, and it has everything you need - from the level of brightness to a responsible app. According to reviews, the bulb runs cool and responds easily through a simple, compatible app. For added comfort and security, the product also works with Nest Protect and Nest Thermostat. It\'s a winner in our books.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>2. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/GE-Wireless-Connected-60-Watt-Equivalent/dp/B00NOL16K0/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">GE Link Connected LED</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/GE-Wireless-Connected-60-Watt-Equivalent/dp/B00NOL16K0/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/31zw0IKIkbL.jpg\" alt=\"GE Wireless Smart Bulb\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAlso a major player in the smart light bulb market is the GE Link. Priced at a comfortable point ($14.97), the bulb is an affordable, attractive bulb that will help connected lighting enter households across the globe. We love the design of the bulb itself - with the bottom half being shiny, white plastic, the top have is like a dome with exposed hardware. It\'s a great, industrial feel, and you can\'t beat the price for a simple, easy to set-up smart light bulb.\r\n<div id=\"tab1\" class=\"rev-content tab\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/GE-Wireless-Connected-60-Watt-Equivalent/dp/B00NOL16K0/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a></div>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"I\'m sure there are other ways people utilize these bulbs, and I\'d love to hear them, but for the above reasons these bulbs are worth much more than $15 a piece to me.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"This is a very cool technology at an affordable entry point\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"This is one sturdy and heavy bulb, the build quality is great. They also look pretty cool. While they seem expensive at first, when you look at other alternatives you realize how well priced they are. I can\'t recommend these enough!\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe love the entry price for this smart light bulb. It truly is affordable for your first attempt at purchasing within the market, and by all accounts it is easy to install and use. Not only does this product offer an impressive design, it also promises easy control and connectivity through the smart phone app. We recommend this product as a starter smart bulb.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>3. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/PHILIPS-426353-Personal-Wireless-Lighting/dp/B00A4EUUO8/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Philips Hue Connected Bulb</a></strong></h3>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/PHILIPS-426353-Personal-Wireless-Lighting/dp/B00A4EUUO8/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51c0TJpNkwL._SL1000_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"708\" /></a></h3>\r\nWe\'re always one for the shock value, so we\'re jumping from an affordable smart home light bulb solution to something that might create sticker shock. Hovering around $200USD,  this Philips Hue Wireless Lighting Bulb is the gem of the market. Not only does it wirelessly control your bulbs, it also lets you customize light color and intensity, while using photos to recreate lighting scenes. AND you can set timers for individual bulbs. It\'s a win/win.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/PHILIPS-426353-Personal-Wireless-Lighting/dp/B00A4EUUO8/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"I love the lights! They\'re definitely not made cheap, and it\'s so easy to set up! So simple and quick! Although the price is quite steep, I do love the product.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"I used it with Tasker to create a sunrise alarm clock!\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"if you are technically-minded (like I am), there is an open API and documentation available to write your own custom software very easily - it\'s a tinkerers dream!\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Philips Hue Connected Bulb is a techie\'s dream. Not only can you create customized light colors and overall intensity (perfect for the home that requires different lighting depending on the room), this product offers plenty of third-party apps on smart-devices (iOS/Android) to do a great deal of command-generated tasks. If you\'re a programmer or power user, this bulb is for you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>4. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/TCP-Connected-Smart-Light-Starter/dp/B00FN6PHRW/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Connected by TCP Smart Lighting System</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/TCP-Connected-Smart-Light-Starter/dp/B00FN6PHRW/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51oU6LOkYUL._SL1500_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"953\" height=\"1500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThis TCP Smart Lighting System it comes with three 11-watt A-Lamp LED light bulbs, a gateway that links to your existing home network and the Internet, an Ethernet cable, and a remote that will let you control the lights manually, should you not want to use your smart phone. It promises to save you money on energy in the long run, while providing easy set-up and management. These bulbs emit soft white light and can dim down to around 5 percent.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Kwikset-Cylinder-Bluetooth-Enabled-Deadbolt/dp/B00CPTD5AQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"The light bulbs themselves are wonderful. Bright, they feel durable and cast a nice light. The connectivity has been consistent, even in my old brick house. \"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"I love these. They work exactly as advertised.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"I love these lights for when we\'re away instead of timers. Easy to set up and use and can be controlled from any device.\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nWe love that this bulb also comes with a remote control. Sometimes, we just want to put our smart phone to rest for an hour or two, and it\'s great to know that you\'ll have that option with this product. But - should you have your smart phone with you - this product works with iOS and Android based systems, and can handle up to 250 devices on 1 system. It\'s a great option at a mid-range price point.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>5. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Cree-Connected-White-Dimmable-Single/dp/B00TN589ZG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Cree Connected LED Bulb</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Cree-Connected-White-Dimmable-Single/dp/B00TN589ZG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51Fvtfl%2BjjL._SL1000_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" /></a>\r\nThe Cree Connected LED Bulb comes to us at an affordable price point, promising functional features and easy-to-install instructions. For its balance of price and overall performance, we love this option as a universal, every day bulb option. It can be controlled anywhere with your Android or iOS device, and uses 81% less energy when compared with an incandescent light bulb. That\'s a huge win in our books.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Cree-Connected-White-Dimmable-Single/dp/B00TN589ZG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"I\'ve been lucky enough to be able play with lots of the different smart bulbs available. All in all, these are my favorite bulb for sure.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"The bulbs certainly look great around my home. They’re lightweight, making them outstanding for ceiling fans or lamp fixtures.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Awesome technology to be able to control the brightness of the bulb, love the dimmable features of it.\" </em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nYou truly cannot go wrong with the Cree Connected LED bulb. This product brings smart lighting to the masses with an affordable price tag, and boasts itself to be an item that\'s simple to set up and control. According to reviews, the white light that this bulb casts is very pleasant, and the quality of the item is said to be high. We love that the Cree Connected LED bulb offers integrated, connected features. We consider this product to be one of the best bets for upgrading your home to smart lighting, while staying within a certain budget.\r\n\r\n<strong>In conclusion...</strong>\r\n\r\nSmart home bulbs are exploding on the market right now, as there are so many different options to choose from. There are so many innovative products and solutions, all with varying price points. At the end of the day, it is important to choose a bulb that works best for you and your home - whether it needs to include dimming features, various lighting options, or both automatic and manual connectivity. These five smart home bulbs are great options for any home.','5 Best Smart Light Bulbs','','draft','open','open','','best-smart-light-bulbs','','','2016-01-08 03:31:50','2016-01-08 03:31:50','',0,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/?p=194',0,'post','',0),
