	(196,6,'2016-01-07 23:33:44','2016-01-07 23:33:44','Just like <a href=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/04/best-smart-home-locks/\" target=\"_blank\">door locks</a>, phones and watches, light bulbs have become significantly more sophisticated over the last few years.\r\n\r\n<em>(If you told your Grandparent that you\'re able to control the light bulb in your home office from your smart phone, what would they say?)</em>\r\n\r\nYour standard light bulb is now being replaced by a number of home connected lighting solutions - solutions that you <strong>can</strong> control with just a few taps on your smart phone device. But with this new advent of connectivity, there are just so many options flooding the market. From disparity in pricing to various feature sets, it can often be hard to determine the best product for your home.\r\n\r\nTo help you make the best decision for your lifestyle, we\'ve compiled five of the best smart light bulbs that we\'ve found. These recommendations are based off research and customer reviews from Amazon, PCMag, WayFair and more.\r\n\r\n<em>Note: Our recommendations are in no particular order. </em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>1. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/LIFX-White-Adjustable-Dimmable-Required/dp/B00XUW0ZFU/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">LIFX White 800 LED Light Bulb</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/LIFX-White-Adjustable-Dimmable-Required/dp/B00XUW0ZFU/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/61D0xHYIesL._SL1250_.jpg\" alt=\"LIFX White Adjustable Light Bulb\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1250\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe LIFX White 800 LED is a bulb that you can control from your smart phone device. This product gives you the ability to personalize your environment, from setting a cool white light during the day or opting for a rich warm glow as you enter the evening. This solution connects to Wi-Fi, and all technology is built within each bulb.  All settings can be adjusted from the app, which is compatible for your smart phone and tablet.\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/LIFX-White-Adjustable-Dimmable-Required/dp/B00XUW0ZFU/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">What Amazon users are saying...</a></strong>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"Setup was much easier than I had expected and the LIFX app was well thought out. You can change the name of each bulb, create groups to control simultaneously, or control each bulb individually!\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>“We have over a dozen in the house and we use them for several different areas. Kids room for fun colors.”</em>\r\n\r\n<em>“Setup could not be more simple. The light is perfect 60watt equiv. brightness. The color temperature can be adjusted which is awesome.”</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nFrom all accounts, this bulb is nearly perfect. It doesn\'t require a hub, and it has everything you need - from the level of brightness to a responsible app. According to reviews, the bulb runs cool and responds easily through a simple, compatible app. For added comfort and security, the product also works with Nest Protect and Nest Thermostat. It\'s a winner in our books.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>2. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/GE-Wireless-Connected-60-Watt-Equivalent/dp/B00NOL16K0/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">GE Link Connected LED</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/GE-Wireless-Connected-60-Watt-Equivalent/dp/B00NOL16K0/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/31zw0IKIkbL.jpg\" alt=\"GE Wireless Smart Bulb\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAlso a major player in the smart light bulb market is the GE Link. Priced at a comfortable point ($14.97), the bulb is an affordable, attractive bulb that will help connected lighting enter households across the globe. We love the design of the bulb itself - with the bottom half being shiny, white plastic, the top have is like a dome with exposed hardware. It\'s a great, industrial feel, and you can\'t beat the price for a simple, easy to set-up smart light bulb.\r\n<div id=\"tab1\" class=\"rev-content tab\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/GE-Wireless-Connected-60-Watt-Equivalent/dp/B00NOL16K0/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a></div>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"I\'m sure there are other ways people utilize these bulbs, and I\'d love to hear them, but for the above reasons these bulbs are worth much more than $15 a piece to me.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"This is a very cool technology at an affordable entry point\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"This is one sturdy and heavy bulb, the build quality is great. They also look pretty cool. While they seem expensive at first, when you look at other alternatives you realize how well priced they are. I can\'t recommend these enough!\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe love the entry price for this smart light bulb. It truly is affordable for your first attempt at purchasing within the market, and by all accounts it is easy to install and use. Not only does this product offer an impressive design, it also promises easy control and connectivity through the smart phone app. We recommend this product as a starter smart bulb.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>3. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/PHILIPS-426353-Personal-Wireless-Lighting/dp/B00A4EUUO8/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Philips Hue Connected Bulb</a></strong></h3>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/PHILIPS-426353-Personal-Wireless-Lighting/dp/B00A4EUUO8/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51c0TJpNkwL._SL1000_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"708\" /></a></h3>\r\nWe\'re always one for the shock value, so we\'re jumping from an affordable smart home light bulb solution to something that might create sticker shock. Hovering around $200USD,  this Philips Hue Wireless Lighting Bulb is the gem of the market. Not only does it wirelessly control your bulbs, it also lets you customize light color and intensity, while using photos to recreate lighting scenes. AND you can set timers for individual bulbs. It\'s a win/win.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/PHILIPS-426353-Personal-Wireless-Lighting/dp/B00A4EUUO8/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"I love the lights! They\'re definitely not made cheap, and it\'s so easy to set up! So simple and quick! Although the price is quite steep, I do love the product.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"I used it with Tasker to create a sunrise alarm clock!\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"if you are technically-minded (like I am), there is an open API and documentation available to write your own custom software very easily - it\'s a tinkerers dream!\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Philips Hue Connected Bulb is a techie\'s dream. Not only can you create customized light colors and overall intensity (perfect for the home that requires different lighting depending on the room), this product offers plenty of third-party apps on smart-devices (iOS/Android) to do a great deal of command-generated tasks. If you\'re a programmer or power user, this bulb is for you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>4. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/TCP-Connected-Smart-Light-Starter/dp/B00FN6PHRW/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Connected by TCP Smart Lighting System</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/TCP-Connected-Smart-Light-Starter/dp/B00FN6PHRW/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51oU6LOkYUL._SL1500_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"953\" height=\"1500\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThis TCP Smart Lighting System it comes with three 11-watt A-Lamp LED light bulbs, a gateway that links to your existing home network and the Internet, an Ethernet cable, and a remote that will let you control the lights manually, should you not want to use your smart phone. It promises to save you money on energy in the long run, while providing easy set-up and management. These bulbs emit soft white light and can dim down to around 5 percent.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Kwikset-Cylinder-Bluetooth-Enabled-Deadbolt/dp/B00CPTD5AQ/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"The light bulbs themselves are wonderful. Bright, they feel durable and cast a nice light. The connectivity has been consistent, even in my old brick house. \"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"I love these. They work exactly as advertised.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"I love these lights for when we\'re away instead of timers. Easy to set up and use and can be controlled from any device.\"</em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nWe love that this bulb also comes with a remote control. Sometimes, we just want to put our smart phone to rest for an hour or two, and it\'s great to know that you\'ll have that option with this product. But - should you have your smart phone with you - this product works with iOS and Android based systems, and can handle up to 250 devices on 1 system. It\'s a great option at a mid-range price point.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>5. <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Cree-Connected-White-Dimmable-Single/dp/B00TN589ZG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Cree Connected LED Bulb</a></strong></h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Cree-Connected-White-Dimmable-Single/dp/B00TN589ZG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51Fvtfl%2BjjL._SL1000_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" /></a>\r\nThe Cree Connected LED Bulb comes to us at an affordable price point, promising functional features and easy-to-install instructions. For its balance of price and overall performance, we love this option as a universal, every day bulb option. It can be controlled anywhere with your Android or iOS device, and uses 81% less energy when compared with an incandescent light bulb. That\'s a huge win in our books.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Cree-Connected-White-Dimmable-Single/dp/B00TN589ZG/&amp;tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>What Amazon users are saying...</strong></a>\r\n<blockquote><em>\"I\'ve been lucky enough to be able play with lots of the different smart bulbs available. All in all, these are my favorite bulb for sure.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"The bulbs certainly look great around my home. They’re lightweight, making them outstanding for ceiling fans or lamp fixtures.\"</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\"Awesome technology to be able to control the brightness of the bulb, love the dimmable features of it.\" </em></blockquote>\r\n<strong>Why we chose it...</strong>\r\n\r\nYou truly cannot go wrong with the Cree Connected LED bulb. This product brings smart lighting to the masses with an affordable price tag, and boasts itself to be an item that\'s simple to set up and control. According to reviews, the white light that this bulb casts is very pleasant, and the quality of the item is said to be high. We love that the Cree Connected LED bulb offers integrated, connected features. We consider this product to be one of the best bets for upgrading your home to smart lighting, while staying within a certain budget.\r\n\r\n<strong>In conclusion...</strong>\r\n\r\nSmart home bulbs are exploding on the market right now, as there are so many different options to choose from. There are so many innovative products and solutions, all with varying price points. At the end of the day, it is important to choose a bulb that works best for you and your home - whether it needs to include dimming features, various lighting options, or both automatic and manual connectivity. These five smart home bulbs are great options for any home.','5 Best Smart Light Bulbs','','inherit','closed','closed','','194-revision-v1','','','2016-01-07 23:33:44','2016-01-07 23:33:44','',194,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/01/07/194-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(197,7,'2016-01-08 00:26:06','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Growing up, many of us thought about “the future” and what it would look like when it arrived. Would it be like <em>The Jetsons</em>, with flying cars and robots as our real life friends? Now, those flying cars haven’t come to fruition yet, and you can’t quite interact with a robot as you would another human… but we do have some pretty amazing inventions on the market today.\r\n\r\nFor a mini taste of the future, why not add a helpful robot to your home’s inventory?\r\n\r\nRobotic vacuums have been around for a while now, but their capabilities have improved vastly over the past couple of years. Not only do they serve as a fun gadget for those of us who consider themselves <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technophilia\">technophiles</a>, but they also cut down on your housework! One of the primary advantages of a robotic vacuum is that you can schedule it to clean your floors as often as you’d like. Most of us don’t have the time (or the interest) in vacuuming our whole house more than once a week. For anyone who suffers from allergies, or families with children and pets who like to make a mess, these little machines can make for a much cleaner space while saving you time. They’re also pretty cool to watch in action, and your kids (and pets) will probably think they’re a blast to watch. You might even get your children interested in housework once they find out robots are involved!\r\n\r\nWe’ve found some of the best reviewed robotic vacuums on the web. Check them out below.\r\n<h2><strong>Best for Value</strong></h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Ecovacs-DEEBOT-D35-Bare-Floor-Cleaning/dp/B010DWI09C/ref=pd_sim_sbs_201_4?ie=UTF8&amp;dpID=41QhLf%2B6UeL&amp;dpSrc=sims&amp;preST=_AC_UL160_SR160%2C160_&amp;refRID=15MGA9VEBAB2H4PDN1WC?tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-201\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-201 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/81VpaMjqNhL._SL1500_-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"81VpaMjqNhL._SL1500_\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" /></a>\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Ecovacs-DEEBOT-D35-Bare-Floor-Cleaning/dp/B010DWI09C/ref=pd_sim_sbs_201_4?ie=UTF8&amp;dpID=41QhLf%2B6UeL&amp;dpSrc=sims&amp;preST=_AC_UL160_SR160%2C160_&amp;refRID=15MGA9VEBAB2H4PDN1WC?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Ecovacs DEEBOT D35 Bare-Floor Cleaning Robot</a></h4>\r\nEcovacs has a well-reviewed line of products at very reasonable prices. The model featured here currently retails for $164.96, which is considerably less than many other robotic vacuums on the market today. This version is made to work on bare/hard floors rather than carpet, but Evovacs makes vacuums that work on carpet as well.\r\n<h4>Evovacs DEEBOT Reviews</h4>\r\nCustomers primarily comment on the great value, speed, and convenience of this vacuum in their reviews on Amazon.com\r\n\r\nOne reviewer’s glowing recommendation: “Wow, what an awesome fast little vacuum!!! I didn\'t purchase this thinking it would keep my house 100% clean but it does!! I purchased this however for one reason. I have bad allergies and I wanted something I could run every few days to help pick up the dust, hair, and other things that just gather in your floor… This one is one of my favorites and the price they are asking is AMAZING.”\r\n<h2><strong>Best for Suction</strong></h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Samsung-VR2AJ9020UG-Powerbot-Essential-Robotic/dp/B0166QEUQ6/ref=sr_1_59?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-59&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Ecovacs-DEEBOT-D35-Bare-Floor-Cleaning/dp/B010DWI09C/ref=pd_sim_sbs_201_4?ie=UTF8&amp;dpID=41QhLf%2B6UeL&amp;dpSrc=sims&amp;preST=_AC_UL160_SR160%2C160_&amp;refRID=15MGA9VEBAB2H4PDN1WC?tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-200\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-200 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/81V2fYNH6L._SL1500_-700x524.jpg\" alt=\"81V2fYN+H6L._SL1500_\" width=\"700\" height=\"524\" /></a>\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Samsung-VR2AJ9020UG-Powerbot-Essential-Robotic/dp/B0166QEUQ6/ref=sr_1_59?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-59&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Ecovacs-DEEBOT-D35-Bare-Floor-Cleaning/dp/B010DWI09C/ref=pd_sim_sbs_201_4?ie=UTF8&amp;dpID=41QhLf%2B6UeL&amp;dpSrc=sims&amp;preST=_AC_UL160_SR160%2C160_&amp;refRID=15MGA9VEBAB2H4PDN1WC?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">Samsung VR2AJ9020UG Powerbot Essential Robotic Vacuum</a></h4>\r\nThis Samsung model is praised for its suction capabilities. It looks more like a traditional vacuum base than many other robotic vacuums, which may be why it is capable of such deep carpet cleaning. It also comes equipped with an electronic mapping system, designed to find the fastest, simplest path for the vacuum to take when cleaning your home. A great choice for families with heavily-trafficked carpets that need an extra deep cleaning.\r\n<h4>Samsung Powerbot Reviews</h4>\r\nReviewers on Amazon.com praise this product for its superior suction capabilities as well as its robotic intelligence.\r\n\r\n“Most of the time, the Powerbot senses something (like a table leg or box), and stops about an inch before it hits it.” One reviewer noted that this model was less likely to crash into household objects, which is a common complaint among robotic vacuum owners.\r\n\r\nAnother reviewer commented that, “the Samsung truly does have much more powerful suction” compared to its competitors.\r\n<h2><strong>Best Vacuum/Mop Combo</strong></h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/bObi-Robotic-Vacuum-Cleaner-Mop/dp/B00XBRYCHG/ref=sr_1_69?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-69&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Samsung-VR2AJ9020UG-Powerbot-Essential-Robotic/dp/B0166QEUQ6/ref=sr_1_59?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-59&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Ecovacs-DEEBOT-D35-Bare-Floor-Cleaning/dp/B010DWI09C/ref=pd_sim_sbs_201_4?ie=UTF8&amp;dpID=41QhLf%2B6UeL&amp;dpSrc=sims&amp;preST=_AC_UL160_SR160%2C160_&amp;refRID=15MGA9VEBAB2H4PDN1WC?tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-198\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-198 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/71sVCzHN9YL._SL1500_-700x700.jpg\" alt=\"71sVCzHN9YL._SL1500_\" width=\"700\" height=\"700\" /></a>\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/bObi-Robotic-Vacuum-Cleaner-Mop/dp/B00XBRYCHG/ref=sr_1_69?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-69&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Samsung-VR2AJ9020UG-Powerbot-Essential-Robotic/dp/B0166QEUQ6/ref=sr_1_59?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-59&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Ecovacs-DEEBOT-D35-Bare-Floor-Cleaning/dp/B010DWI09C/ref=pd_sim_sbs_201_4?ie=UTF8&amp;dpID=41QhLf%2B6UeL&amp;dpSrc=sims&amp;preST=_AC_UL160_SR160%2C160_&amp;refRID=15MGA9VEBAB2H4PDN1WC?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">bObi Robotic Vacuum Cleaner and Mop</a></h4>\r\nThis cute little robot is a multi-tasker that can be used to sweep, vacuum, and mop your floors efficiently. It comes with several attachments which allow you to switch between vacuuming and mopping. Great for families whose homes have a variety of floor types who need multiple cleaning options.\r\n\r\nCustomer reviews are overwhelmingly positive, and we love the sleek and modern design of this product.\r\n<h4>bObi Reviews</h4>\r\nOne customer on Amazon.com puts it simply. “A friend got us a Bobi and it has really added convenience to our lives. We have hardwood floors and two dogs, so it seemed like we were always sweeping! Now we just let Bobi run around the house and all of the dog hair and dirt gets picked up. It\'s so nice to come home to a swept floor!”\r\n\r\nThe bObi offers convenience, a sleek design, and great results.\r\n<h2><strong>Best for Allergies &amp; Pet Hair </strong></h2>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/bObi-Robotic-Vacuum-Cleaner-Mop/dp/B00XBRYCHG/ref=sr_1_69?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-69&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Samsung-VR2AJ9020UG-Powerbot-Essential-Robotic/dp/B0166QEUQ6/ref=sr_1_59?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-59&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Ecovacs-DEEBOT-D35-Bare-Floor-Cleaning/dp/B010DWI09C/ref=pd_sim_sbs_201_4?ie=UTF8&amp;dpID=41QhLf%2B6UeL&amp;dpSrc=sims&amp;preST=_AC_UL160_SR160%2C160_&amp;refRID=15MGA9VEBAB2H4PDN1WC?tag=ideaing-20\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-199\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-199 size-large\" src=\"http://ideaing.dev//ideas/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/81ePyZTISSL._SL1500_-700x774.jpg\" alt=\"81ePyZTISSL._SL1500_\" width=\"700\" height=\"774\" /></a>\r\n<h4><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/iRobot-Cleaning-Allergies-Brushes-together/dp/B00OBWQI3Q/ref=sr_1_66?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-66&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/bObi-Robotic-Vacuum-Cleaner-Mop/dp/B00XBRYCHG/ref=sr_1_69?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-69&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Samsung-VR2AJ9020UG-Powerbot-Essential-Robotic/dp/B0166QEUQ6/ref=sr_1_59?s=vacuums&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1452125884&amp;sr=1-59&amp;keywords=robot+vacuumhttp://www.amazon.com/Ecovacs-DEEBOT-D35-Bare-Floor-Cleaning/dp/B010DWI09C/ref=pd_sim_sbs_201_4?ie=UTF8&amp;dpID=41QhLf%2B6UeL&amp;dpSrc=sims&amp;preST=_AC_UL160_SR160%2C160_&amp;refRID=15MGA9VEBAB2H4PDN1WC?tag=ideaing-20\" target=\"_blank\">iRobot Roomba 880 Vacuum Cleaning Robot For Pets and Allergies</a></h4>\r\nOne of the main reasons people want to purchase a robotic vacuum is because they have to frequently vacuum their family pet’s hair. Having a robotic vacuum allows you to schedule a cleaning as many times as needed throughout the week, and saves you the time it would take to complete your daily cleaning requirements. This is also important for allergy sufferers, whose conditions are often set off by dust and hair around the house.\r\n\r\nThe Roomba featured here is pricier than the other products on this list, but comes with extra attachments and a boatload of great customer reviews.\r\n<h4>iRobot Roomba 880 Reviews</h4>\r\nCustomer’s on Amazon.com have reviewed the Roomba with overwhelmingly positive marks. Many people say that the product has dramatically helped their allergies, and that pet hair around there house has been heavily reduced.\r\n\r\nThis customer says that the product cleans even better than a human doing the same work! “There are a few great things about this that make it BETTER than a human cleaner (1) it can get under tables and chairs so you don\'t have to move all of the furniture to clean (2) it reaches corners that are out of sight (3) unlike using a normal vacuum or a broom, it does not kick dust and fur up into the air as it cleans.”\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLet’s face it, a vacuum cleaner isn’t often considered a “fun” purchase… but these robotic versions actually make the idea of housecleaning fun and interesting. As technology expands, we’ll likely see more common household tasks being taken over by robots. That’s something that, based on the glowing reviews left on these products, many consumers will welcome with open arms. What’s better than a neat gadget that saves you time and increases your home’s technology quotient?\r\n\r\nIn fact, LG just announced a brand new robotic vacuum, <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2015/12/21/lgs-robotic-vacuum-is-both-janitor-and-security-guard/\" target=\"_blank\">the Turbo+</a>, that will release in 2016. Their product doubles as a home security camera to help detect intruders. As technology continues to advance, we can expect to see more and more developments like this one: multi-tasking, high tech, home assistants. The way of the future!','The Best Robotic Vacuums','','draft','open','open','','the-best-robotic-vacuums','','','2016-01-08 00:26:06','2016-01-08 00:26:06','',0,'http://ideaing.dev//ideas/?p=197',0,'post','',0),
